1
00:00:37,990 --> 00:00:41,120
好，来吧，专心
OK... Here we go. Focus.

2
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:44,560
速度，我就是速度
Speed. I am speed.

3
00:00:46,270 --> 00:00:49,000
一位冠军，42位失败者
One winner, 42 losers.

4
00:00:49,070 --> 00:00:51,630
我会把失败者当早餐吃掉的
I eat losers for breakfast.

5
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:55,180
早餐
Breakfast.

6
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:57,340
稍等，也许我已经吃过早餐了
Wait, maybe I should have had breakfast.

7
00:00:57,410 --> 00:01:01,110
稍微休息一下也不错\n不不不，专注，加速
A little breck-y could be good for me. No, no, no, stay focused. Speed.

8
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:05,050
疾上加疾，快上加快
I'm faster than fast. Quicker than quick.

9
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:06,710
我就是“闪电”！
I am lightning!

10
00:01:07,860 --> 00:01:10,150
喂，“闪电”，准备好了吗
Hey, Lightning! You ready?

11
00:01:11,790 --> 00:01:14,960
喔耶，“闪电”已经准备好了
Oh, yeah. Lightning's ready

12
00:01:32,580 --> 00:01:34,980
哦，我有话要讲

13
00:01:53,230 --> 00:01:54,330
咔嚓！
Ka-chow!

14
00:02:07,609 --> 00:02:10,120
片名：汽车总动员
Cars 2006

15
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:43,510
卖天线球喔
Get your antenna balls here!

16
00:02:50,090 --> 00:02:52,250
冲啊，“闪电”！
Go, Lightnin'!

17
00:02:52,330 --> 00:02:56,320
- 哇喔！\n- 说的没错，伙计
- Whoo! - You got that right, slick.

18
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:25,160
欢迎回到狄纳哥400
Welcome back to the Dinoco 400.

19
00:03:25,230 --> 00:03:28,860
我是鲍伯凯特拉斯\n以及我的好友岱洛卡崔普
I'm Bob Cutlass, here with my good friend, Darrell Cartrip.

20
00:03:28,930 --> 00:03:31,920
赛车史上一场至关重要的比赛正在进行之中
We're midway through what may be an historic day for racing.

21
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:34,030
鲍伯，我的油压现在高到不行
Bob, my oil pressure's through the roof.

22
00:03:34,100 --> 00:03:37,700
如果再继续这样剌激下去\n我就得被拖吊出去了！
If this gets more exciting, they're gonna have to tow me outta the booth!

23
00:03:37,770 --> 00:03:38,830
没错，岱洛
Right, Darrell.

24
00:03:38,910 --> 00:03:41,540
三位选手以平分的方式
Three cars are tied for the season points lead,

25
00:03:41,610 --> 00:03:43,700
进入今年的总决赛
heading into the final race of the season.

26
00:03:43,780 --> 00:03:48,550
赢得这场比赛的人\n不仅得到年度总冠军，更将得到活塞杯
And the winner of this race will win the season title and the Piston Cup.

27
00:03:48,620 --> 00:03:50,310
绰号“国王”的选手史崔普惠特
Does The King, Strip Weathers,

28
00:03:50,390 --> 00:03:52,790
会在退役之前再得到一项冠军吗？
have one more victory in him before retirement?

29
00:03:52,850 --> 00:03:55,450
他一向都是狄纳哥的常胜将军
He's been Dinoco's golden boy for years!

30
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,720
他能否再赢一次活塞杯呢？
Can he win them one last Piston Cup?

31
00:03:57,790 --> 00:04:01,160
像往常一样\n别忘了第二名的选手奇克希克斯
And, as always, in the second place spot we find Chick Hicks.

32
00:04:01,230 --> 00:04:03,750
他的整个职业生涯\n都一直紧咬着“国王”不放
He's been chasing that tailfin his entire career.

33
00:04:03,830 --> 00:04:05,990
奇克认为今年时机已到
Chick thought this was his year.

34
00:04:06,070 --> 00:04:08,830
也许他可以从“国王”的阴影下走出来
His chance to finally emerge from The King's shadow.

35
00:04:08,900 --> 00:04:12,960
但他意想不到的是\n“闪电”麦坤！
But the last thing he expected was... Lightning McQueen!

36
00:04:13,040 --> 00:04:15,670
我想大家都没预料到这种情况
You know, I don't think anybody expected this.

37
00:04:15,740 --> 00:04:18,370
赛季开始时麦坤只是个无名小卒
The rookie sensation came into the season unknown.

38
00:04:18,450 --> 00:04:19,940
但现在没有人不认识他了
But everyone knows him now.

39
00:04:20,010 --> 00:04:24,080
他会成为第一个赢得\n活塞杯的新人并入主迪纳哥吗？
Will he be the first rookie to win a Piston Cup and land Dinoco?

40
00:04:24,190 --> 00:04:26,750
传奇“国王”，凶猛“路霸”，新人“闪电”！
The legend, the runner-up, and the rookie!

41
00:04:26,820 --> 00:04:29,690
三辆赛车，一个冠军！
Three cars, one champion!

42
00:04:41,870 --> 00:04:43,360
你休想！
No you don't.

43
00:04:46,070 --> 00:04:48,070
嘿！
Hey!

44
00:04:55,050 --> 00:04:56,950
开得太棒了！
What a ride!

45
00:04:58,350 --> 00:05:00,550
追上去，麦坤！\n追上去！
Go get 'em, McQueen! Go get 'em!

46
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:06,190
我爱你，“闪电”！
I love you, Lightning!

47
00:05:06,260 --> 00:05:08,920
迪纳哥是我的！
Dinoco is all mine.

48
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,930
第三个弯脚处有麻烦了！
Trouble, turn three!

49
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:14,230
- 看你怎么过来，麦坤\n- 领先者的后面发生了大碰撞
- Get through that, McQueen. - Huge crash behind the leaders!

50
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:38,990
等等，岱洛\n麦坤冲进了混乱之中
Wait a second, Darrell. McQueen is in the wreckage.

51
00:05:39,060 --> 00:05:41,890
他不可能穿过那里的！
There's no way the rookie can make it through!

52
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,190
他会被撞烂的
Not in one piece, that is.

53
00:05:57,810 --> 00:05:59,510
耶！
Yeah!

54
00:05:59,580 --> 00:06:01,550
“闪电”！喔！
Lightning! Oh!

55
00:06:03,450 --> 00:06:05,920
快看啊！麦坤冲出来了
Look at that! McQueen made it through!

56
00:06:05,990 --> 00:06:08,460
“闪电”麦坤又一次上演精彩表演
A spectacular move by Lightning McQueen!

57
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:10,650
耶！咔嚓！
Yeah! Ka-chow!

58
00:06:10,730 --> 00:06:13,990
“闪电”！“闪电”！“闪电”！
McQueen! McQueen! McQueen! McQueen! McQueen! McQueen!

59
00:06:14,060 --> 00:06:17,030
耶，麦坤！咔嚓！
Yeah, McQueen! Ka-chow!

60
00:06:17,100 --> 00:06:19,330
当大家都进入维修站的时候
While everyone heads into the pits,

61
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:21,160
只有麦坤留在赛道上保持领先
McQueen stays out to take the lead!

62
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:24,230
别把我拖出去，教练\n我还能比赛！
Don't take me out, coach. I can still race!

63
00:06:28,980 --> 00:06:31,450
觉得怎么样？漂亮吧
What do you think? A thing of beauty.

64
00:06:31,510 --> 00:06:33,450
- 麦坤出来了！\n- 什么？
- McQueen made it! - What?

65
00:06:33,510 --> 00:06:34,570
他没有进站！
He's not pitting!

66
00:06:34,650 --> 00:06:37,780
你们得让我出去\n快点！我要去追他！
You gotta get me out there! Let's go! Get me back out there!

67
00:06:37,850 --> 00:06:39,620
麦坤没有进站！
McQueen's not going into the pits!

68
00:06:39,690 --> 00:06:43,250
这个新人解雇了他的领队\n这赛季的第三个了！
The rookie fired his crew chief. The third this season!

69
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:45,620
- 看起来他喜欢单干\n- 冲，冲啊！
- Says he likes working alone. - Go, go!

70
00:06:45,690 --> 00:06:47,920
看来奇克在维修站里耽误了不少时间
Looks like Chick got caught up in the pits.

71
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:51,400
对呀，像这样的的停站\n他有的路要赶了
Yeah, after a stop like that, he's got a lot of ground to make up.

72
00:06:51,470 --> 00:06:53,870
准备好，伙计们\n比赛要重新开始了
Get ready, boys, we're coming to the restart!

73
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,850
让开，让开，让开！
Come on, come on, come on!

74
00:07:22,230 --> 00:07:24,320
我们需要换胎！\n伙计们，快点！
We need tires now! Come on, let's go!

75
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:27,100
- 不，不，不，不！不要换胎，只要加油\n- 什么？
- No, no, no, no! No tires, just gas! - What?

76
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:29,290
你需要新轮胎呀，白痴！
You need tires, you idiot!

77
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:32,610
看来麦坤今天只加油就好了
Looks like it's gas-and-go's for McQueen today.

78
00:07:32,670 --> 00:07:34,110
对呀，又不换轮胎
Right. No tires again.

79
00:07:34,180 --> 00:07:36,870
通常那只会给你带来短暂的优势\n但之后会害了你的
That's a short-term gain, long-term loss,

80
00:07:36,940 --> 00:07:40,610
不过看起来这对麦坤不适用\n嘿，看来他比我们懂的还多
but it's workin' for him. He obviously knows somethin' we don't know.

81
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:52,960
快结束了，岱洛，比赛剩下最后一圈\n麦坤领先了一大截
This is it, Darrell. One lap to go and Lightning McQueen has a huge lead.

82
00:07:53,030 --> 00:07:55,890
他的冠军已经手到擒来了\n可以把啦啦队叫出来欢呼了吧！
He's got it in the bag. Call in the dogs and put out the fire!

83
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:58,260
我们有一个新冠军了！
We're gonna crown us a new champion!

84
00:08:04,740 --> 00:08:06,970
终点线，我来啦！
- Checkered flag, here I come!

85
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:09,030
糟糕！麦坤爆胎了！
No! McQueen's blown a tire!

86
00:08:09,110 --> 00:08:11,840
只剩最后一个弯，他到的了吗？
And with only one turn to go! Can he make it?

87
00:08:11,910 --> 00:08:14,470
你这个笨蛋！
- You fool!

88
00:08:15,850 --> 00:08:18,320
麦坤爆胎了！他爆胎了！
McQueen's blown a tire! He's blown a tire!

89
00:08:18,390 --> 00:08:19,880
快追快追！
Go, go, go!

90
00:08:29,060 --> 00:08:30,790
他又爆了另一个胎！
He's lost another tire!

91
00:08:30,870 --> 00:08:34,100
- “国王”和“路霸”快速拉近距离！\n- 他们一起进入三号弯脚
- King and Chick come up fast! - They're entering turn three!

92
00:08:34,170 --> 00:08:36,030
加油
Come on.

93
00:08:37,910 --> 00:08:40,140
真是难以置信，鲍伯！
I don't believe what I'm watching, Bob!

94
00:08:40,210 --> 00:08:43,740
“闪电”麦坤和他的活塞杯奖座只差一百尺！
Lightning McQueen is 100 feet from his Piston Cup!

95
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:52,080
“国王”和“路霸”过了四号个弯
The King and Chick rounding turn four.

96
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:58,220
最后一段了\n冠军是...冠军是
Down the stretch they come! And it's, and it's...

97
00:08:58,290 --> 00:09:01,090
- 太紧凑了，相差太小了\n- 简直不敢相信！
- It's too close to call! Too close! - I don't believe it!

98
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:02,530
“闪电”！
Lightning!

99
00:09:02,830 --> 00:09:05,820
- 最最引人入胜，最最精彩的...\n- 真不敢相信！
- The most spectacular, amazing... - I don't believe it!

100
00:09:05,900 --> 00:09:09,360
史上最精彩的结局！
...unequivocally, unbelievable ending in the history of the world!

101
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:11,460
- 我们都不知道谁获得了冠军！\n- 看啊！
- And we don't know who won! - Look at that!

102
00:09:22,150 --> 00:09:25,180
- 这太接近了\n- 能再放一遍吗？
- That's very close to call. - Can we play that again?

103
00:09:25,250 --> 00:09:27,450
嘿，不准拍照！出去！
Hey, no cameras! Get outta here!

104
00:09:27,590 --> 00:09:30,060
我们在冠军通道等待最终结果
We're here in Victory Lane, awaiting the results.

105
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:32,590
麦坤，刚才你不换车胎实在是太大胆了
McQueen, that was a risky move, not taking tires.

106
00:09:32,660 --> 00:09:33,650
你倒是说说
Tell me about it!

107
00:09:33,730 --> 00:09:36,390
你会不会后悔\n你没有维修团队呢
Are you sorry you didn't have a crew chief out there?

108
00:09:36,460 --> 00:09:39,900
喔，可莉\n赛车不是只顾输赢就好的
Oh, Kori. There's a lot more to racing than just winning.

109
00:09:39,970 --> 00:09:43,870
如果我轻易的领先一整圈夺冠\n那还有什么意思
I mean, taking the race by a full lap... Where's the entertainment in that?

110
00:09:43,940 --> 00:09:45,870
我要给观众们剌激感呀
I wanted to give folks a little sizzle.

111
00:09:45,940 --> 00:09:48,070
- 剌激？\n- 我会后悔没有维修队吗？
- Sizzle? - Am I sorry I don't have a crew chief?

112
00:09:48,140 --> 00:09:50,300
不，当然不会\n因为我自己一人就搞定了
No, I'm not. 'Cause I'm a one-man show.

113
00:09:50,380 --> 00:09:51,810
什么？喔，好吧
What? Oh, yeah, right.

114
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:53,940
真有自信的“闪电”麦坤
That was a confident Lightning McQueen.

115
00:09:54,020 --> 00:09:56,640
从终点线为您带来的时况转播\n我是可莉特布瓦茨
Live from Victory Lane, I'm Kori Turbowitz.

116
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:58,410
- 喂，闪开\n- 嘿，查克
- Get outta the shot. - Yo, Chuck.

117
00:09:58,490 --> 00:10:00,180
查克你在干嘛？\n你挡住摄影机了！
Chuck, what are you doing? You're blockin' the camera!

118
00:10:00,250 --> 00:10:02,250
- 大家都想看闪电\n- 什么？
- Everyone wants to see the bolt. - What?

119
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:05,920
- 退后退后\n- 就是这样！快，伙计们
- Now, back away. - That's it! Come on, guys.

120
00:10:05,990 --> 00:10:10,050
- 唉呀，你们这是干嘛\n- 我们不干了你！自己一人搞定吧
- Whoa, team! Where are you going? - We quit, Mr. One-Man Show!

121
00:10:10,130 --> 00:10:11,830
喔喔，随便吧
Oh, OK, leave. Fine.

122
00:10:11,900 --> 00:10:15,670
要再找到一个能\n帮我加油的人很难吗？
How will I ever find anyone else who knows how to fill me up with gas?

123
00:10:16,800 --> 00:10:19,710
- 再见，查克\n- 我不叫查克！
- Adios, Chuck! - And my name is not Chuck!

124
00:10:19,770 --> 00:10:21,440
哦，随便吧
Oh, whatever.

125
00:10:21,510 --> 00:10:23,530
喂，麦坤！叫你呢，麦坤！
Hey, Lightning! Yo! McQueen!

126
00:10:23,610 --> 00:10:26,910
刚才的比赛可真漂亮啊
Seriously, that was some pretty darn nice racin' out there.

127
00:10:26,980 --> 00:10:29,210
- 我是说我！\n- 嗯，好吧
- By me! - Oh, yeah.

128
00:10:29,280 --> 00:10:31,810
- 太棒了！\n- 欢迎来到奇克时代！
- Zinger! - Welcome to the Chick era, baby!

129
00:10:31,890 --> 00:10:34,550
不过活塞杯是我的，伙计，是我的
The Piston Cup... It's mine, dude. It's mine.

130
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:39,180
我觉得迪纳哥蓝蛮适合我的，迪纳哥蓝！
Hey, fellas, how do you think I'd look in Dinoco blue? Dinoco blue!

131
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:41,090
你做你的白日梦吧，“雷”先生
In your dreams, Thunder.

132
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:44,260
哈，没错，“雷”？\n他干嘛叫我“雷”？
Yeah, right. Thunder? What's he talkin' about, "Thunder"?

133
00:10:44,330 --> 00:10:47,170
喔，你知道\n打雷一向都是在闪电之后啊
You know, 'cause thunder always comes after lightning.

134
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:49,030
咔乒！咔乓！
Ka-ping! Ka-pow!

135
00:10:49,100 --> 00:10:51,540
- 你们谁了解雷吗？\n- 不清楚
- Who knew about the thunder thing? - I didn't.

136
00:10:51,610 --> 00:10:53,300
- 我们要闪电！\n- 这就对了！
- Give us the bolt! - That's right.

137
00:10:53,370 --> 00:10:54,840
往右转，对着镜头
Right in the lens.

138
00:10:55,010 --> 00:10:57,170
- 伙计，秀一下闪电！\n- 笑一个，麦坤！
- Show me the bolt, baby! - Smile, McQueen!

139
00:10:57,250 --> 00:11:00,540
- 秀一下闪电，麦坤！\n- 就是这样！
- Show me the bolt, McQueen! - That's it!

140
00:11:05,850 --> 00:11:10,310
比赛结果太接近了\n迪纳哥以你为荣
That was one close finish. You sure made Dinoco proud.

141
00:11:10,390 --> 00:11:11,380
谢谢你，“国王”
Thank you, King.

142
00:11:11,460 --> 00:11:14,220
泰仕，这些年你一直对我很好
Well, Tex, you've been good to me all these years.

143
00:11:14,300 --> 00:11:15,660
我只是尽全力去比赛而已
It's the least I could do.

144
00:11:15,730 --> 00:11:18,960
不管结果怎样\n你永远都是我的冠军
Whatever happens, you're a winner to me, you old daddy rabbit.

145
00:11:19,030 --> 00:11:21,830
谢了，亲爱的\n没有你我什么都做不成
Thanks, dear. Wouldn't be nothing without you.

146
00:11:21,900 --> 00:11:23,600
咔嚓！
Kch-i-ka-chow!

147
00:11:24,670 --> 00:11:26,330
- 我是蜜亚\n- 我是蒂亚
- I'm Mia. - I'm Tia.

148
00:11:26,410 --> 00:11:29,670
我们是你的头号粉丝！\n咔嚓！
We're, like, your biggest fans! Ka-chow!

149
00:11:29,740 --> 00:11:32,240
我爱做自己！
I love being me.

150
00:11:32,310 --> 00:11:35,410
- 好了，女孩们，可以了\n- 我们爱你，“闪电”！
- OK, girls, that's it. - We love you, Lightning!

151
00:11:37,390 --> 00:11:40,220
小子，你真是个胆大的选手
Hey, buddy. You're one gutsy racer.

152
00:11:40,290 --> 00:11:41,850
噢，“国王”先生你好
Oh, hey, Mr. The King.

153
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:43,720
你拥有的天份是其它选手
