00:27:16,690 --> 00:27:19,420
记者现在洛杉矶国际赛道为您实况转播
We're live at the Los Angeles International Speedway

319
00:27:19,490 --> 00:27:22,020
第一位选手“闪电”麦坤
as the first competitor, Lightning McQueen,

320
00:27:22,100 --> 00:27:24,390
现在已经到达了
is arriving at the track.

321
00:27:24,460 --> 00:27:26,400
他要去和赛车女郎约会的事是真的吗？
Is it true he's gonna pose for Cargirl?

322
00:27:26,470 --> 00:27:27,630
你的战略是什么？
What's your strategy?

323
00:27:29,670 --> 00:27:32,370
怎么啦？我忘了擦我的挡泥板吗？
What? Did I forget to wipe my mud flaps?

324
00:27:33,910 --> 00:27:37,270
麦坤的司机到了加州，但麦坤却失踪了
McQueen's driver arrived in California, but McQueen was missing.

325
00:27:37,340 --> 00:27:41,300
赛车“闪电麦坤”失踪\n而他却应该在几天后参加空前的比赛
- McQueen was reported missing. ...to race an unprecedented...

326
00:27:41,380 --> 00:27:43,940
赞助商公开声明不知道他在哪里
Sponsor stated they have no idea where he is.

327
00:27:46,890 --> 00:27:50,380
我希望“闪电”没事\n希望他别碰上了麻烦
I hope Lightning's OK. I'd hate to see anything bad happen to him.

328
00:27:50,460 --> 00:27:54,660
不知道谁比较难找\n“闪电”麦坤或是他的维修队长
I don't know what's harder to find, McQueen or a chief who'll work with him!

329
00:27:54,730 --> 00:27:57,820
我们一定要尽全力找到“闪电”麦坤！
Lightning McQueen must be found at all costs!

330
00:27:57,900 --> 00:28:01,860
每个人都在问相同的问题\n麦坤在哪里？
They're all asking the same question: Where is McQueen?

331
00:28:02,840 --> 00:28:05,000
哦，伙计
Oh, boy.

332
00:28:06,010 --> 00:28:08,130
我在哪里？
Where am I?

333
00:28:08,280 --> 00:28:10,800
- 早啊，睡美人！\n- 啊！
- Mornin', sleepin' beauty! - Ah!

334
00:28:11,510 --> 00:28:14,000
我去烧个水你就醒过来了
Boy, I was wonderin' when you was gonna wake up.

335
00:28:14,080 --> 00:28:16,780
你想要什么都给你\n不要伤害我
Take whatever you want! Just don't hurt me!

336
00:28:17,050 --> 00:28:19,750
轮胎锁？\n为什么我的轮胎被锁上了
A parking boot? Why do I have a parking boot on?

337
00:28:19,820 --> 00:28:24,780
- 发生了什么事？\n- 你真有意思
- What's going on here? Please! - You're funny.

338
00:28:24,860 --> 00:28:27,920
我已经开始喜欢你了，我叫拖线
I like you already. My name's Mater.

339
00:28:29,430 --> 00:28:30,420
拖线？
Mater?

340
00:28:30,500 --> 00:28:33,430
对呀\n就像少根筋的意思
Yeah, like "tuh-mater," but without the "tuh".

341
00:28:33,500 --> 00:28:36,770
- 你叫什么名字？\n- 你不知道我名字？
- What's your name? - You don't know my name?

342
00:28:36,840 --> 00:28:37,830
呃...
Uh...

343
00:28:37,900 --> 00:28:41,310
不知道...你也叫拖线？
No, I know your name. Is your name Mater too?

344
00:28:41,370 --> 00:28:42,400
什么？
What?

345
00:28:42,480 --> 00:28:47,240
我必须要赶去加州\n我现在在哪里？
Look, I need to get to California as fast as possible. Where am I?

346
00:28:47,310 --> 00:28:49,580
你在哪里？啊哈
Where are you? Shoot!

347
00:28:49,650 --> 00:28:51,210
你在水乡温泉镇
You're in Radiator Springs.

348
00:28:51,280 --> 00:28:54,690
这是一个漂亮的小镇
The cutest little town in Carburetor County.

349
00:28:54,750 --> 00:28:57,620
噢，太棒了\n真是太棒了
Oh, great. Just great!

350
00:28:57,690 --> 00:29:02,220
如果你觉得这样就棒的话\n你该去看看镇上其它地方
Well, if you think that's great, you should see the rest of the town.

351
00:29:02,300 --> 00:29:06,100
说真的，我很想去看看其它地方
You know, I'd love to see the rest of the town!

352
00:29:06,300 --> 00:29:09,130
所以你把门打开，解开我的锁
So if you could just open the gate, take this boot off,

353
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:11,930
我们两个一起去逛逛吧看看附近的好景点
you and me, we go cruisin', check out the local scene...

354
00:29:12,010 --> 00:29:14,240
- 太棒了\n- 会是什么样的景色呢？
- Dad-gum! - How'd that be, Tuhmater?

355
00:29:14,310 --> 00:29:15,830
- 酷！\n- 拖线！
- Cool! - Mater!

356
00:29:15,910 --> 00:29:18,780
我不是叫你不要跟犯人说话的嘛？
What did I tell you about talkin' to the accused?

357
00:29:18,850 --> 00:29:20,340
不说话
To not to.

358
00:29:20,410 --> 00:29:24,850
那你就快闭嘴\n把他拖去交通法庭吧
Well, quit your yappin' and tow this delinquent road hazard to traffic court.

359
00:29:24,920 --> 00:29:27,010
好吧，我们晚点再聊，拖线
Well, we'll talk later, Mater.

360
00:29:27,090 --> 00:29:29,950
再聊，拖线,真好笑
"Later, Mater." That's funny!

361
00:29:30,220 --> 00:29:31,210
啊！
Ah!

362
00:29:31,290 --> 00:29:34,990
水乡温泉镇交通法院\n现在开庭
The Radiator Springs Traffic Court will come to order!

363
00:29:35,060 --> 00:29:38,590
嘿，你刮坏了我的漆！\n我要揍扁你
Hey, you scratched my paint! I oughta take a blowtorch to you, man!

364
00:29:38,670 --> 00:29:41,070
你把道路弄坏了！\n你是一辆罪恶深重的车
You broke-a the road! You a very bad car!

365
00:29:41,130 --> 00:29:42,160
- 法西斯！\n- 共产党！
- Fascist! - Commie!

366
00:29:42,240 --> 00:29:44,930
警官，你能不能告诉我这要开多久
Officer, talk to me, babe. How long is this gonna take?

367
00:29:45,010 --> 00:29:46,770
我必须赶去加州
I gotta get to California, pronto.

368
00:29:46,840 --> 00:29:48,000
你的律师呢？
Where's your lawyer?

369
00:29:48,070 --> 00:29:51,340
不知道，大概跑去大溪地了吧\n他在那边租了个渡假村
I don't know. Tahiti maybe. He's got a timeshare there.

370
00:29:51,410 --> 00:29:56,540
他如果被控没有律师的话\n法院将指派一位律师给他
When a defendant has no lawyer, the court will assign one to him. Hey!

371
00:29:56,620 --> 00:29:58,610
喂，有没有人想当他的律师啊？
Anyone want to be his lawyer?

372
00:29:59,990 --> 00:30:02,320
好吧，让我来，韩大夫
Shoot, I'll do it, Sheriff!

373
00:30:02,390 --> 00:30:06,160
起立，今天的法官是韩大夫
All rise! The Honorable Doc Hudson presiding.

374
00:30:06,490 --> 00:30:07,620
炫耀狂
Show-off.

375
00:30:07,690 --> 00:30:11,030
祷告韩大夫对你手下留情吧
May Doc have mercy on your soul.

376
00:30:11,100 --> 00:30:12,290
好啊
All right,

377
00:30:12,370 --> 00:30:15,490
我想知道\n到底是谁把我的镇搞成这样
I wanna know who's responsible for wreckin' my town, Sheriff.

378
00:30:15,570 --> 00:30:17,470
我要把他的引擎盖拆下来
I want his hood on a platter!

379
00:30:17,540 --> 00:30:20,200
我要把他关在牢里直到他腐烂
I'm gonna put him in jail till he rots! No, check that.

380
00:30:20,270 --> 00:30:24,040
我要把他关在牢里\n直到监狱都垮下来
I'm gonna put him in jail till the jail rots on top of him,

381
00:30:24,110 --> 00:30:27,770
然后把他移到另一个监狱\n直到另一个监狱也垮下来
and then I'm gonna move him to a new jail and let that jail rot.

382
00:30:27,850 --> 00:30:29,370
我还要
I'm...

383
00:30:31,350 --> 00:30:33,290
把他丢出去，警长
Throw him out of here, Sheriff.

384
00:30:33,350 --> 00:30:36,720
把他丢出我的法庭\n把他赶出我的镇
I want him out of my courtroom. I want him out of our town!

385
00:30:36,860 --> 00:30:38,450
- 结案\n- 太好了
- Case dismissed. - Yes!

386
00:30:38,530 --> 00:30:40,790
嘿，我这个辩护律师做得不错嘛
Boy, I'm purty good at this lawyerin' stuff.

387
00:30:40,860 --> 00:30:42,330
不好意思我迟到了，法官大人
Sorry I'm late, Your Honor!

388
00:30:43,360 --> 00:30:47,360
哇，保时捷，她一定是我的律师派来的
Holy Porsche! She's gotta be from my attorney's office.

389
00:30:47,430 --> 00:30:49,900
喂，谢谢你赶来\n不过这案子已经解决了
Hey, thanks for comin', but we're all set.

390
00:30:49,970 --> 00:30:52,400
- 他无罪释放了我\n- 他无罪释放你？
- He's letting me go. - He's letting you go?

391
00:30:52,470 --> 00:30:54,410
对呀，你今天的工作轻松吧
Yeah, your job's pretty easy today.

392
00:30:54,470 --> 00:30:57,640
你现在只要站在那边让我好好看着你
All you have to do now is stand there and let me look at you.

393
00:30:57,710 --> 00:31:01,270
听好，我直说吧\n我跟你一起去吃晚餐吧，咔嚓
Listen, I'm gonna cut to the chase. Me, you, dinner. Pi-cha-kow!

394
00:31:01,680 --> 00:31:03,310
- 什么？哦！啊！\n- 咔嚓！
- What the...? Ow! Oh! - Ka-chow!

395
00:31:03,380 --> 00:31:06,440
- 拜托！\n- 没关系，我了解你的感受
- Please! - I know. I get that reaction a lot.

396
00:31:06,590 --> 00:31:10,110
我常常让别人感受到前所未有的感觉
I create feelings in others that they themselves don't understand.

397
00:31:10,190 --> 00:31:11,850
啊！哦！
Agh! Ow!

398
00:31:11,930 --> 00:31:14,330
不好意思，我吓到你了吗？
Oh, I'm sorry. Did I scare you?

399
00:31:14,390 --> 00:31:16,420
有一点，不过我没事
A little bit, but I'll be all right.

400
00:31:16,500 --> 00:31:20,260
呃，我去跟法官谈谈
OK. I'm gonna go talk to the judge.

401
00:31:20,330 --> 00:31:22,930
去吧，宝贝，不过小心点
Do what you gotta do, baby. But listen. Be careful.

402
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:26,700
这里的人脑袋都有点秀逗\n如果你知道我的意思
Folks around here are not firing on all cylinders, if you know what I mean.

403
00:31:26,810 --> 00:31:28,770
咔嚓！
Ka-ching!

404
00:31:28,840 --> 00:31:29,930
啊！
Ah!

405
00:31:30,080 --> 00:31:32,010
谢谢你的忠告
I'll keep that in mind.

406
00:31:32,180 --> 00:31:34,580
- 你好啊，拖线\n- 你好呀，莎莉
- Hey there, Mater. - Howdy, Sally.

407
00:31:34,950 --> 00:31:37,250
- 大家好\n- 早安
- Hi, folks! - Good morning!

408
00:31:37,980 --> 00:31:38,970
你认识她？
You know her?

409
00:31:39,050 --> 00:31:42,020
她是镇上的律师\n也是我的未婚妻
She's the town attorney and my fiancee.

410
00:31:42,090 --> 00:31:43,080
什么？
What?

411
00:31:43,160 --> 00:31:47,250
开玩笑的\n她只喜欢我的外表
Nah, I'm just kiddin'. She just likes me for my body.

412
00:31:47,330 --> 00:31:51,160
韩大夫，您今天看起来真帅\n你是不是改装了你的后照镜？
You look great. You do something different with your side view mirrors?

413
00:31:51,230 --> 00:31:52,890
你到底想说什么，莎莉
What do you want, Sally?

414
00:31:52,970 --> 00:31:56,330
求求你，判他修理被破坏的道路\n我们镇上需要道路啊
Come on, make this guy fix the road. The town needs this.

415
00:31:56,400 --> 00:31:59,570
不行，我看多了他这种人，赛车
No. I know his type. Racecar.

416
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:01,700
这镇上最不需要的就是赛车
That's the last thing this town needs.

417
00:32:01,780 --> 00:32:06,270
好吧，我本来不想这样，是你逼我的
OK, I didn't want to have to do this, Doc, but you leave me no choice.

418
00:32:06,350 --> 00:32:10,280
各位好市民，你们一定都熟悉这镇上\n令人引以为傲的历史吧
Fellow citizens, you're all aware of our town's proud history.

419
00:32:10,350 --> 00:32:11,780
她又来了
Here she goes again.

420
00:32:11,850 --> 00:32:14,550
水乡温泉镇
Radiator Springs, the glorious jewel

421
00:32:14,620 --> 00:32:18,250
是俗称道路之母的66号公路上
strung on the necklace of Route 66, the mother road!

422
00:32:18,320 --> 00:32:22,120
一颗闪亮的宝石\n我们有权利也有义务
It is our job and our pleasure to take care of the travelers

423
00:32:22,200 --> 00:32:25,190
- 照顾所有穿过这城镇的旅行者\n- 旅行者？什么旅行者？
- on our stretch of that road. - Travelers? What travelers?

424
00:32:25,270 --> 00:32:26,430
不要理他
Ignore him.

425
00:32:26,500 --> 00:32:29,870
可是我问你们，现在路被弄坏了\n我们要怎么照顾这些旅行者
But how, I ask you, are we to care for those travelers

426
00:32:29,940 --> 00:32:32,270
如果没有路给他们开了？
if there is no road for them to drive on?

427
00:32:32,340 --> 00:32:35,140
- 路易奇，你的店里卖什么？\n- 轮胎
- Luigi, what do you have at your store? - Tires.

428
00:32:35,210 --> 00:32:36,700
但如果没有路可以到达你的店呢？
And if no one can get to you?

429
00:32:36,780 --> 00:32:41,110
那我的轮胎就卖不出去\n我什么都没有了
I won't sell any... tires. I will lose everything!

430
00:32:41,180 --> 00:32:44,010
- 芙蓉，你的店里卖什么？\n- 我卖汽油
- Flo, what do you have at your store? - I have gas.

431
00:32:44,080 --> 00:32:47,480
- 很多汽油！\n- 好的，伙计们，听我说
- Lotsa gas! - OK boys, stay with me.

432
00:32:47,550 --> 00:32:51,080
芙蓉，如果没有人能到达你的店加油呢？
And, Flo, what'll happen if no one can come to your station to buy gas?

433
00:32:51,160 --> 00:32:54,650
那我会\n被迫关店而搬走
I'll go outta business and... we'll have to leave town.

434
00:32:54,730 --> 00:32:57,860
如果芙蓉关了加油站搬走了我们怎么办？
What's gonna happen if Flo leaves town and closes her station?

435
00:32:57,930 --> 00:33:00,490
- 没有汽油，我们也不能动了\n- 什么？
- Without gas, we're done for! - What?

436
00:33:00,570 --> 00:33:03,400
所以你们不觉得闯祸的人\n应该负责修理吗？
Don't you think the car responsible should fix our road?

437
00:33:03,470 --> 00:33:06,700
可是唯一够强壮修路的人是大阿尔呀
The only guy strong enough to fix that road is Big Al!

438
00:33:06,770 --> 00:33:09,000
丽姬，阿尔15年前就搬走了
Lizzie, Big Al left like, 15 years ago.

439
00:33:09,080 --> 00:33:11,100
那你干嘛还提他的名字？
Then why are you bringing him up, you lemon?

440
00:33:11,180 --> 00:33:12,170
哦，他能办到
Oh, he can do it.

441
00:33:12,250 --> 00:33:15,040
没问题的，他可以修路\n他马力足够，所以你们想要他做什么？
He's got the horsepower. So, what do you want him to do?

442
00:33:15,110 --> 00:33:16,580
修理马路！
Fix the road!

443
00:33:16,650 --> 00:33:20,210
- 因为我们的城镇是值得修补的！\n- 没错！
- Because we are a town worth fixing! - Yeah!

444
00:33:21,620 --> 00:33:24,820
肃静
Order in the court!

445
00:33:25,590 --> 00:33:28,360
看来有人帮我改变了决定
Seems like my mind has been changed for me.

446
00:33:28,430 --> 00:33:30,420
- 好哇\n- 不要啊
- Yeah! - No!

447
00:33:30,500 --> 00:33:31,830
判得好
Nice ruling.

448
00:33:32,570 --> 00:33:36,060
我不邀请你共进晚餐了
Oh, I am so not taking you to dinner.

449
00:33:36,140 --> 00:33:40,000
哈，没关系\n你可以带贝茜去
That's OK, Stickers. You can take Bessie.

450
00:33:40,210 --> 00:33:41,900
哇，你可以跟贝茜共事！
Man, you get to work with Bessie!

451
00:33:41,980 --> 00:33:44,600
我也好希望能跟她一起工作
I'd give my left two lug nuts for somethin' like that.

452
00:33:44,680 --> 00:33:47,340
贝茜？贝茜是谁？
Bessie? Who's Bessie?

453
00:33:49,550 --> 00:33:53,510
这就是贝茜\n镇上最好的铺路机
This here is Bessie, finest road-pavin' machine ever built.

454
00:33:53,590 --> 00:33:56,650
我现在判你做社区服务
I'm hereby sentencing you to community service.

455
00:33:56,720 --> 00:33:59,450
你要在我的监督下修理马路
You're gonna fix the road under my supervision.

456
00:33:59,530 --> 00:34:01,860
什么，这是什么鬼地方！
What? This place is crazy!

457
00:34:01,930 --> 00:34:04,090
喂，我知道现在提这个不好
I know this may be a bad time right now,

458
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:07,160
可是你欠我三万两千元律师费
but you owe me $32,000 in legal fees.

459
00:34:07,230 --> 00:34:08,220
什么？
What?

460
00:34:08,300 --> 00:34:11,860
我们会把贝茜接在你后面\n你要对她温柔点
We're gonna hitch you up to Bessie, and you're gonna pull her nice.

461
00:34:11,940 --> 00:34:13,530
开什么玩笑
You gotta be kidding me.

462
00:34:13,610 --> 00:34:16,270
你从路的那头开始
You start there where the road begins.

463
00:34:16,640 --> 00:34:19,640
然后到路的那头结束
You finish down there where the road ends.

464
00:34:21,610 --> 00:34:23,880
天哪！
Holy shoot!

465
00:34:24,420 --> 00:34:26,820
喂，喂，喂\n这样要做多久？
Whoa, whoa, whoa! How long is this gonna take?

466
00:34:26,890 --> 00:34:30,450
只要不下雨的话\n大概五天
Well, fella does it right, should take him about five days.

467
00:34:30,520 --> 00:34:31,680
五天？
Five days?

468
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:34,690
我现在应该已经在加州\n谈迪纳哥的事呢！
But I should be in California schmoozing Dinoco right now!

469
00:34:34,760 --> 00:34:37,730
那你更该赶快闭嘴开始工作
Then if I were you, I'd quit yappin' and start workin'!

470
00:34:37,800 --> 00:34:40,290
- 把他接起来吧，拖线\n- 好的好的
- Hook him up, Mater. - Okay-dokey.

471
00:34:48,370 --> 00:34:50,600
自由啦！
Freedom!

472
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:59,440
也许我该先把他接上贝茜
Maybe I should've hooked him up to Bessie...

473
00:35:00,220 --> 00:35:03,520
再解开锁的
...and then... then took the boot off.

474
00:35:04,990 --> 00:35:07,390
哈呼！
Whoo-hoo!

475
00:35:08,130 --> 00:35:12,120
再见啦，水乡温泉镇\n再见，贝茜
Goodbye, Radiator Springs, and goodbye, Bessie!

476
00:35:12,200 --> 00:35:16,070
加州，我来了！耶！
California, here I come! Yeah!

477
00:35:18,440 --> 00:35:20,430
风吹的感觉真舒服
Oh, feel that wind.

478
00:35:20,870 --> 00:35:22,470
太棒了
Yes!

479
00:35:23,640 --> 00:35:25,670
不不不不
No. No, no, no.

480
00:35:25,980 --> 00:35:28,280
不不不不，没油了
No, no, no, no, no. Outta gas?

481
00:35:28,350 --> 00:35:30,340
我怎么会没油了
How can I be outta gas?

482
00:35:30,420 --> 00:35:34,380
小子，我们没你想像中那么笨
Boy, we ain't as dumb as you think we are.

483
00:35:34,450 --> 00:35:36,790
可，可，可是，你们怎么
But how did, how did... you...?

484
00:35:36,860 --> 00:35:39,190
我们趁你昏迷的时候\n把你的汽油吸出来的
We siphoned your gas while you were passed out.

485
00:35:39,260 --> 00:35:42,160
- 咔嚓\n- 噢噢噢
- Ka-chow. - Ow, ow, ow, ow.

486
00:35:50,570 --> 00:35:52,970
- 各位\n- 警长
- Gentlemen. - Sheriff.

487
00:35:53,040 --> 00:35:54,130
嘿，警长
Hey, Sheriff.

488
00:35:54,210 --> 00:35:56,470
- 轮胎为什么在这里？\n- [意大利语]
- Why here? - [Italian] Sono sempre stati qui.

489
00:35:56,540 --> 00:35:59,030
- 他们在原来的地方比较好\n- [意大利语]
- They were better before. - Stai sempre a parlare.

490
00:35:59,110 --> 00:36:00,980
- 戈里多\n- 小红，你能不能移过去一点
- Guido! - Red, can you move over?

491
00:36:01,050 --> 00:36:03,880
我想看看那台性感赛车
I want to get a look at that sexy hot rod.

492
00:36:03,950 --> 00:36:06,780
你知道吗，我以前也是蛮风光的
You know, I used to be a purty good whistler.

493
00:36:06,850 --> 00:36:09,580
当然现在不成啦
I can't do it now, of course, on account of sometimes

494
00:36:09,660 --> 00:36:12,560
老，引擎积水，不中用
I get fluid built up in my engine block,

495
00:36:12,630 --> 00:36:15,990
韩大夫说他会帮我修理\n他什么都能修
but Doc said he's gonna fix it. He can fix about anything.

496
00:36:16,060 --> 00:36:18,290
就是这样我们才选他做法官的
That's why we made him the judge.

497
00:36:18,460 --> 00:36:22,630
孩子，你应该听我说过了
Boy, you shoulda heard me on Giddy-up, Oom Papa Mow Mow.

498
00:36:22,700 --> 00:36:24,070
我可没吹牛
Now, I'm not one to brag

499
00:36:24,140 --> 00:36:27,440
别人都大老远来看我
but people come purty far to see me get low on the "Mow-Mow".

500
00:36:27,910 --> 00:36:28,930
哦！
Oh!

501
00:36:29,010 --> 00:36:31,840
- 啊，伙计，天啊！\n- 喂，怎么了
- Aw, man, that's just great! - Hey, what's wrong?

502
00:36:31,910 --> 00:36:33,710
我的幸运贴纸脏了
My lucky sticker's all dirty.

503
00:36:33,780 --> 00:36:36,040
噢，没关系\n我帮你洗洗
Ah, that ain't nothin'. I'll clean it for ya.

504
00:36:36,120 --> 00:36:40,810
不不不！
No, no, no!

505
00:36:40,890 --> 00:36:43,220
不用了
That won't be necessary.

506
00:36:44,290 --> 00:36:47,590
嘿！嘿！大家伙\n没错，就是你，红色的
Hey! Hey, big fella! Yeah, you in the red!

507
00:36:47,660 --> 00:36:50,290
你能不能帮我冲洗一下呀
I could use a little hose down. Help me wash this off.

508
00:36:52,730 --> 00:36:53,720
他跑哪去了？
Where's he goin'?

509
00:36:53,800 --> 00:36:57,240
他呀，他有点害羞嘛\n而且他很气你把他的花搞砸了
Oh, he's a little bit shy, and he hates you for killin' his flowers.

510
00:36:57,300 --> 00:36:58,830
为什么我要受这种气
I shouldn't put up with this.

511
00:36:58,910 --> 00:37:01,770
我是一个结合速度与流线的精密仪器
I'm a precision instrument of speed and aerodynamics.

512
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:04,870
- 你“遗弃”什么？\n- 我是一辆很有名的赛车！
- You hurt your what? - I'm a very famous racecar!

513
00:37:05,140 --> 00:37:08,340
你是有名的赛车？真的赛车？
You are a famous racecar? A real racecar?

514
00:37:08,410 --> 00:37:11,040
对呀，当然是真的\n不然咧，瞧瞧我
Yes, I'm a real racecar. What do you think? Look at me.

515
00:37:11,120 --> 00:37:15,110
我最喜欢赛车了\n我从小就爱看
I have followed racing my entire life. My whole life!

516
00:37:15,190 --> 00:37:17,490
那你一定认识我\n我是“闪电”麦坤
Then you know who I am. I'm Lightning McQueen.

517
00:37:17,560 --> 00:37:19,650
- “闪电”麦坤？\n- 是啊！没错！
- Lightning McQueen? - Yes! Yes!

518
00:37:19,730 --> 00:37:21,720
我高兴得想尖叫
I must scream it to the world!

519
00:37:21,790 --> 00:37:26,030
这实在太剌激了！
My excitement from the top of someplace very high!

520
00:37:26,100 --> 00:37:28,590
- 你认识很多法拉利吗？\n- 不不不不不
- Do you know many Ferraris? - No, no, no, no, no.

521
00:37:28,670 --> 00:37:31,640
他们是在欧洲的赛道比赛\n我是在活塞杯
They race on the European circuit. I'm in the Piston Cup!

522
00:37:32,410 --> 00:37:35,340
- 什么？\n- 路易奇只看法拉利赛车
- What? - Luigi follow only the Ferraris.

523
00:37:40,210 --> 00:37:42,770
我没看错吧？
Is that what I think it is?

524
00:37:44,350 --> 00:37:45,610
顾客
Customers.

525
00:37:45,690 --> 00:37:49,140
各位，有顾客来了！
Customers! Customers, everyone! Customers!

526
00:37:49,220 --> 00:37:50,590
- 好\n- 顾客？
- OK! - Customers?

527
00:37:50,660 --> 00:37:53,490
我知道已经过了很久，但我们排练过的
Been a long time. Remember what we rehearsed.

528
00:37:53,560 --> 00:37:56,120
记得把你的“营业中”招牌朝向外面
Make sure your "Open, please come in" signs are out.

529
00:37:56,200 --> 00:37:59,720
其它的你们都会吧\n好的，别紧张，我们开始吧
You all know what to do. All right, nobody panics. Here we go!

530
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:02,460
连恩，我没看到高速公路入口啊
Van, I just don't see any on-ramp anywhere.

531
00:38:02,540 --> 00:38:06,940
- 米妮，我知道我们在哪里\n- 对对对，我们在一个不知名的地方
- Minny, I know exactly where we are. - Yeah, we're in the middle of nowhere.

532
00:38:07,010 --> 00:38:09,670
- 甜心，别这样\n- 你们好
- Honey, please. - Hello.

533
00:38:09,740 --> 00:38:12,710
欢迎到水乡温泉镇\n饰谷的入口镇
Welcome to Radiator Springs, gateway to Ornament Valley.

534
00:38:12,780 --> 00:38:15,040
我们以亲切的服务和友善的态度闻名
Legendary for its service and hospitality.

535
00:38:15,110 --> 00:38:16,140
有什么需要帮助的吗？
How can we help you?

536
00:38:16,220 --> 00:38:20,280
- 不用了，谢谢你\n- 问问她到州际公路怎么走
- We don't need anything, thank you. - Ask for directions to the Interstate.

537
00:38:20,350 --> 00:38:23,580
不用问，我知道该怎么走
There's no need to ask for directions. I know where we're going.

538
00:38:23,660 --> 00:38:26,090
我们上次去沙克比的时候他也是这样
He did the same thing on our trip to Shakopee.

539
00:38:26,160 --> 00:38:28,990
我们那时候还是疯狂的年轻人
We were headed over there for the Crazy Days, and we...

540
00:38:29,060 --> 00:38:32,120
- 好啦好啦，不要再说了\n- 你们需要什么？
- OK. Really. We're just peachy, OK? - What you really need

541
00:38:32,200 --> 00:38:36,260
香甜的有机汽油
is the sweet taste of my homemade, organic fuel.

542
00:38:36,340 --> 00:38:38,030
不了，我的肚子不同意
No, it doesn't agree with my tank.

543
00:38:38,100 --> 00:38:41,300
- 我们只想找到州际公路\n- 你好呀，阿兵哥
- Just trying to find the Interstate. - Good to see you, soldier!

544
00:38:41,370 --> 00:38:44,710
请来摄巨的剩余物品店
Come on by Sarge's Surplus Hut for your government surplus needs.

545
00:38:44,780 --> 00:38:47,110
- 亲爱的，补给啊!\n- 我们的补给太多了
- Honey, surplus! - We have too much surplus.

546
00:38:47,180 --> 00:38:49,510
我们的舒适小椎旅馆有地图唷
I do have a map over at the Cozy Cone Motel.

547
00:38:49,580 --> 00:38:52,750
如果你们待一晚的话\n我们还会免费附送早餐
And if you stay, we offer a free Lincoln Continental breakfast.

548
00:38:52,820 --> 00:38:56,550
- 老公，她有地图耶\n- 我才不需要地图，我有卫星导航系统
- Honey, she's got a map. - I don't need a map! I have the GPS.

549
00:38:56,620 --> 00:39:00,080
- 永远不用再看地图了，谢谢\n- 要喝点什么吗？
- Never need a map again, thank you. - How 'bout somethin' to drink?

550
00:39:00,160 --> 00:39:04,100
请来芙蓉的V8小栈坐坐\n66公路上最纯的汽油喔
Stop at Flo's V-Eight Cafe. Finest fuel on Route 66.

551
00:39:04,160 --> 00:39:05,320
不用了，我们刚加满油
No we just topped off.

552
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:09,270
如果你们需要轮胎的话\n请到路易奇的凯萨斜塔轮胎店
And if you need tires, stop by Luigi's Casa Della Tires,

553
00:39:09,340 --> 00:39:11,800
有世界闻名的轮胎塔
home of the Leaning Tower of Tires.

554
00:39:11,870 --> 00:39:15,200
- 我们只想找到州际公路\n- 可是您需要重新烤漆
- We're trying to find the Interstate. - But you do need a paint job.

555
00:39:15,270 --> 00:39:18,440
雷蒙会帮你烤个好漆\n什么样式颜色都行
Ramone will paint you up right. Hey, anything you want!

556
00:39:18,510 --> 00:39:20,810
- 例如火焰形啦\n- 不，谢谢
- You know, like a flame job. - No thanks...

557
00:39:20,880 --> 00:39:22,210
例如鬼火啦
Maybe ghost flames!

558
00:39:22,280 --> 00:39:24,840
或是您喜欢传统的线条纹？\n凡达奇款式？
You like old school pinstripin'? Von Dutch style?

559
00:39:24,920 --> 00:39:28,820
老公，你看，凡达奇
Oh, honey, look. Von Dutch.

560
00:39:28,890 --> 00:39:31,910
不，够了，我们要走了好吗
OK, no. We're gonna be going now, OK?

561
00:39:31,990 --> 00:39:33,480
喔！
Ow!

562
00:39:33,560 --> 00:39:36,760
送你个纪念品，要记得回来唷
A little somethin' to remember us by, OK?

563
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:39,090
- 好吧\n- 要再来唷
- OK! - Come back soon, OK?

564
00:39:39,170 --> 00:39:42,660
你知道我们在哪里的\n别忘了告诉你们的朋友们
I mean, you know where we are! Tell your friends!

565
00:39:44,270 --> 00:39:46,330
呵呵呵，好
OK! Yes. You bet.

566
00:39:46,410 --> 00:39:48,670
谢啦，拜拜
Thanks again, folks. Bye-bye now.

567
00:39:48,740 --> 00:39:51,840
喂喂喂喂
Psst! Psst! Hey! Hey, hey, hey!

568
00:39:51,910 --> 00:39:54,070
- 我知道怎么到州际公路\n- 是吗
- I know how to get to the Interstate! - Do ya?

569
00:39:54,150 --> 00:39:56,810
- 米妮，不要理他\n- 对啊对啊
- Minny, no. - Yeah, yeah, yeah.

570
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:58,350
呃，其实我不知道，听着
No, not really. But listen.

571
00:39:58,420 --> 00:40:02,050
我是“闪电”麦坤，著名的赛车\n我被强制拘禁在这里
I'm Lightning McQueen, famous racecar. I'm being held against my will.

572
00:40:02,120 --> 00:40:04,650
你们要帮我个忙，打给我的队员\n叫他们来教我
I need you to call my team, so they can come rescue me

573
00:40:04,720 --> 00:40:08,560
我才能赶回加州，参加活塞杯\n明白吗？
and get me to California in time for me to win the Piston Cup. Understand?

574
00:40:09,530 --> 00:40:11,790
不不不不不不不
No, no, no, no, no, no, no.

575
00:40:11,860 --> 00:40:15,730
是真的啊，不骗你\n你们一定要帮我离开这儿
No, it's the truth! I'm telling you! You gotta help me! Don't leave me here!

576
00:40:15,800 --> 00:40:18,960
这个满是乡巴佬的小镇\n我的IQ在直线下降！
I'm in hillbilly hell! My IQ's dropping by the second!

577
00:40:19,040 --> 00:40:21,130
我要变得跟他们一样了！
I'm becoming one of them!

578
00:40:23,010 --> 00:40:25,140
别烦恼了\n他们知道我们在哪里了
OK, don't worry. They know where we are now.

579
00:40:25,210 --> 00:40:26,970
他们会帮我们宣传的，等着瞧吧
They'll tell friends. You'll see.

580
00:40:27,050 --> 00:40:29,910
“闪电”麦坤还是不见踪影
We'll be back for our Hank Williams marathon...

581
00:40:29,980 --> 00:40:32,710
很好，自活塞杯赛事升级之后
- That's good. ...after a Piston Cup update.

582
00:40:32,790 --> 00:40:36,690
仍然没有“闪电”麦坤\n到达加州的迹象
Still no sign of Lightning McQueen. Chick arrived in California

583
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:40,210
今天第一辆赛车已经开始适应场地了
and today became the first car to spend practice time on the track.

584
00:40:40,290 --> 00:40:43,460
这种领先别人先到赛场的感觉真棒
It's nice to get out here before the other competitors.

585
00:40:43,530 --> 00:40:47,300
你知道嘛，领先一步\n是个好采头
You know, get a head start. Gives me an edge.

586
00:40:50,740 --> 00:40:52,530
哈哈哈！
Hoo-hoo-hoo!

587
00:40:57,610 --> 00:40:58,600
哈哈！
Ha-ha!

588
00:41:02,450 --> 00:41:03,440
耶！
Yeah!

589
00:41:15,060 --> 00:41:17,390
喂，麦坤\n别太伤心了
Hey, McQueen... Eat your heart out.

590
00:41:17,860 --> 00:41:19,690
哦！
Oh!

591
00:41:19,770 --> 00:41:21,130
我直说吧
Let me get this straight.

592
00:41:21,200 --> 00:41:24,140
我把路修好就可以走了，对吧？
I can go when this road is done. That's the deal, right?

593
00:41:24,200 --> 00:41:27,930
- 对啊，他们是这么说的\n- 好，让路让路
- That's what they done did said. - OK. Outta my way.

594
00:41:28,010 --> 00:41:29,100
我要修路了
I got a road to finish.

595
00:41:40,950 --> 00:41:43,350
- 他修完了\n- 修完了？
- He's done! - Done?

596
00:41:43,420 --> 00:41:45,790
- 是啊\n- 才过一个小时而已
- Uh-huh. - It's only been an hour.

597
00:41:47,730 --> 00:41:51,060
啊，我做完了，做完了
Ah, I'm done. Look, I'm finished.

598
00:41:51,130 --> 00:41:54,000
现在你们只要跟我道谢\n我就走人了
Say thanks, and I'll be on my way. That's all you gotta say.

599
00:41:54,600 --> 00:41:58,260
哈！我第一个开在新路上
Whee-hoo! I'm the first one on the new road!

600
00:41:58,840 --> 00:42:00,430
哦！
Oh!

601
00:42:01,770 --> 00:42:04,470
看起来好丑啊
It rides purty smooth.

602
00:42:04,710 --> 00:42:08,170
- 看上去好难看！\n- 跟你们这个镇蛮配的
- It looks awful! - Well, it matches the rest of the town.

603
00:42:08,280 --> 00:42:11,770
哦！
- Oh!

604
00:42:12,150 --> 00:42:14,140
小红
Red.

605
00:42:16,760 --> 00:42:18,090
你以为你是谁啊
Who do you think you are?

606
00:42:18,160 --> 00:42:21,460
喂，韩大夫说我做完后我就可以走的
Look, Doc said when I finish, I could go. That was the deal.

607
00:42:21,530 --> 00:42:24,960
我说的是把路铺好\n不是弄得更糟
The deal was you fix the road, not make it worse.

608
00:42:25,030 --> 00:42:27,500
把它刮起来，重铺一遍
Now, scrape it off! Start over again.

609
00:42:27,570 --> 00:42:31,200
老爹，我可不是铲土机，我是个赛车耶
Hey, look, grandpa, I'm not a bulldozer. I'm a racecar.

610
00:42:31,270 --> 00:42:32,760
哇喔
Oh-ho-ho-ho!

611
00:42:32,840 --> 00:42:37,070
是吗？要不我们来个比赛怎么样？\n就我们两个
Is that right? Then why don't we just have a little race? Me and you.

612
00:42:37,140 --> 00:42:40,940
- 什么？\n- 我跟你，你在开玩笑吗？
- What? - Me and you. That a joke?

613
00:42:41,010 --> 00:42:43,380
如果你赢了，你就可以走\n我自己修路
If you win, you go and I fix the road.

614
00:42:43,450 --> 00:42:46,150
如果我赢的话\n你得照我的方式修路
If I win, you do the road my way.

615
00:42:46,220 --> 00:42:47,740
韩大夫，你在说什么呀
Doc, what're you doin'?

616
00:42:48,120 --> 00:42:49,950
不好意思喔
I don't mean to be rude here,

617
00:42:50,020 --> 00:42:53,750
不过你从0到60里恐怕要开个3年半吧
but you probably go zero to sixty in, like, what? Three-point-five years?

618
00:42:53,830 --> 00:42:56,350
那我想你应该没什么好怕的吧
Then I reckon you ain't got nothin' to worry about.

619
00:42:56,430 --> 00:43:01,090
好吧，既然你这么说\n那就来比一场吧
You know what, old-timer? That's a wonderful idea. Let's race.

620
00:43:02,840 --> 00:43:05,360
两位，这场比赛只有一圈
Gentlemen, this will be a one-lap race.

621
00:43:05,440 --> 00:43:09,930
你们要开到威利丘，绕过丘再折返回来
You will drive to Willy's Butte, go around Willy's Butte and come back.

622
00:43:10,010 --> 00:43:12,940
不可以碰撞，做弊吐口水
There will be no bumpin', no cheatin', no spittin',

623
00:43:13,010 --> 00:43:15,540
不许咬人，发飙，乱放油，推拖
no bitin', no road rage, no maimin',

624
00:43:15,610 --> 00:43:20,750
不许暗箭伤人，独占道路
no oil slickin', no pushin', no shovin', no backstabbin', no road-hoggin',

625
00:43:20,820 --> 00:43:22,580
不许横冲直撞
and no lollygaggin'.

626
00:43:22,660 --> 00:43:24,210
速度，我就是速度
Speed. I'm speed.

627
00:43:24,290 --> 00:43:26,850
壮如凯迪拉克，快如宝马
Float like a Cadillac, sting like a Beemer.

628
00:43:28,090 --> 00:43:32,890
我的梦想就是参与赛车比赛
My friend Guido, he dream to give a real racecar a pit stop.

629
00:43:32,970 --> 00:43:35,490
- 加油维修区！\n- 呃...
- Peet stop! - Uh...

630
00:43:35,570 --> 00:43:38,440
伙计，这场比赛只有一圈
The race is only one lap, guys.

631
00:43:38,500 --> 00:43:41,000
一圈而已！不需要你们的帮忙
Uno lappo! Don't need any help.

632
00:43:41,070 --> 00:43:44,910
- 有我就搞定了\n- 哼，随便你
- I work solo mio. - Fine. Race your way.

633
00:43:46,210 --> 00:43:50,080
- 不用加油维修，了解吗？\n- 好吧
- No pit stoppo. Comprendo? - OK.

634
00:43:50,180 --> 00:43:52,170
两位
Gentlemen...

635
00:43:52,820 --> 00:43:55,650
发动你们的引擎
...start your engines!

636
00:44:02,430 --> 00:44:04,790
- 都看看吧！\n- 哇
- Hijole! Check that out! - Whoa.

637
00:44:04,860 --> 00:44:07,960
韩大夫，你的馊主意\n现在路永远修不好了
Great idea, Doc. Now the road will never get done.

638
00:44:08,330 --> 00:44:09,630
路易奇？
Luigi?

639
00:44:09,700 --> 00:44:12,900
各就各位，预备，开始！
On your mark, get set...

640
00:44:12,970 --> 00:44:15,200
为了奖金，应该秀一下了
Uno for the money, due for the show,

641
00:44:15,270 --> 00:44:20,970
准备，难以置信，冲啊！
tre to get ready, and quattro to... I can't believe it. Go!

642
00:44:29,460 --> 00:44:30,790
嗯？
Huh?

643
00:44:31,420 --> 00:44:33,950
韩大夫，摇旗就是说冲啊
Doc... the flag means go.

644
00:44:34,030 --> 00:44:37,360
没错，摇旗\n我们出发吧，出发
Remember the fl... Here we go. Go.

645
00:44:37,430 --> 00:44:40,160
韩大夫，你在干嘛
Doc, what are you doing, man?

646
00:44:40,230 --> 00:44:43,790
真糟，看来我晚了一步
Oh, dear. It would seem I'm off to a poor start.

647
00:44:43,870 --> 00:44:47,000
不过再迟也比不跑好，走吧，拖线
Well, better late than never. Come on, Mater.

648
00:44:47,070 --> 00:44:49,840
- 可能需要你的帮忙\n- 呃...好吧
- Might need a little help. - Uh... OK.

649
00:44:51,540 --> 00:44:52,980
你有带拖吊工具吧？
You got your tow cable?

650
00:44:53,050 --> 00:44:55,240
当然有啦\n为什么？
Well, yeah, I always got my tow cable. Why?

651
00:44:55,310 --> 00:44:57,610
只是预防万一
Oh, just in case.

652
00:45:06,160 --> 00:45:08,350
哇噢哇噢\n噢！噢！噢！噢！噢！
Ow! Ow! Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow.

653
00:45:08,430 --> 00:45:10,160
不不不不不！
No, no, no, no, no!

654
00:45:10,300 --> 00:45:12,700
- 哦，天啊！\n- 哇
- Oh, man! - Whoa.

655
00:45:13,430 --> 00:45:15,730
- 哦！\n- 够糟的吧，伙计
- Ow! - Bad trip, man.

656
00:45:18,900 --> 00:45:24,900
嘿！这就是你说的“重”如凯迪拉克或是“笨”如宝马跑车？
Hey! Was that floatin' like a Cadillac or was that stingin' like a Beemer?

657
00:45:24,980 --> 00:45:27,340
我搞糊涂了
I'm confused.

658
00:45:27,410 --> 00:45:29,510
你开车就像你修路一样
You drive like you fix roads.

659
00:45:29,580 --> 00:45:32,780
技术真糙！玩笑开够了，拖线
Lousy! Have fun fishin', Mater.

660
00:45:36,590 --> 00:45:38,420
啊！
Ah!

661
00:45:39,160 --> 00:45:42,130
原来韩大夫早就知道你会失控
I'm startin' to think he knowed you was gonna crash!

662
00:45:42,190 --> 00:45:45,320
谢了，拖线，谢谢
Thank you, Mater. Thank you.

663
00:45:48,430 --> 00:45:50,370
那种小弯对我应该不算什么啊
I can make a little turn on dirt.

664
00:45:50,440 --> 00:45:51,870
你觉得呢？
You think?

665
00:45:51,940 --> 00:45:56,400
不，我又浪费了一天\n我是不是永远逃不出这里了！
No. And now I'm a day behind. I'm never gonna get outta here!

666
00:45:56,480 --> 00:45:58,940
嘿，放松点\n你需要新的烤漆，伙计
Hey, ese! You need a new paint job, man!

667
00:45:59,010 --> 00:46:01,980
- 不了，谢谢\n- 有机燃料呢？
- No, thank you. - How 'bout some organic fuel?

668
00:46:02,050 --> 00:46:04,410
- 那恶心的果汁？\n- 算了吧
- That freak juice? - Pass.

669
00:46:04,480 --> 00:46:08,940
唔，看他工作的样子让我口干舌燥\n有没有人要喝饮料呀？
Whoo! Watchin' him is makin' me thirsty. Anybody else want somethin' to drink?

670
00:46:09,020 --> 00:46:10,610
不用了，芙蓉
Nah, not me, Flo.

671
00:46:10,690 --> 00:46:13,160
因为我是一个特殊机器
I'm on one of them there special diets.

672
00:46:13,230 --> 00:46:17,820
我是结合速度与“空洞”的精密仪器
I'm a precisional instrument of speed and aero-matics.

673
00:46:18,400 --> 00:46:20,660
“你开车像你修路”
"You race like you fix roads."

674
00:46:20,730 --> 00:46:25,500
我会，给他好看！
I'll show him. I will show him!

675
00:46:33,850 --> 00:46:38,180
气死我啦！
Oh, great! I hate it!

676
00:46:38,250 --> 00:46:41,880
- 气死了！气死了！气死了！\n- 这声音真是太美妙了
- Hate, hate, hate, hate it! - Music. Sweet music.

677
00:46:43,090 --> 00:46:45,650
也许这么做不太好
Maybe this wasn't such a good idea.

678
00:46:45,720 --> 00:46:48,450
水乡温泉镇，快乐的地方！
Radiator Springs, a happy place!

679
00:46:48,530 --> 00:46:51,550
好啊，贝茜，你觉得我很幽默吗？
OK, Bessie, you think that's funny?

680
00:46:54,100 --> 00:46:57,900
好啊！我竟然和贝茜说话了！\n我和贝茜说话了！
Great! I'm talking to Bessie now! I'm talking to Bessie!

681
00:47:10,950 --> 00:47:12,010
哇
Wow.

682
00:47:12,350 --> 00:47:14,050
早安，莎莉
Mornin', Sally!

683
00:47:14,120 --> 00:47:19,320
嘿，你们快来看看这条漂亮的新路\n“闪电”麦坤铺的喔
Hey, look at this here fancy new road that Lightnin' McQueen done just made!

684
00:47:19,390 --> 00:47:21,420
真的耶，不可思议
Yes! Uh, amazing!

685
00:47:21,890 --> 00:47:25,520
哇！耶！
Whoa-ho! Yeah!

686
00:47:25,600 --> 00:47:29,800
唔，雷蒙！好久没看到你那么有精神了
Oh, Ramone! Mama ain't seen you that low in years.

687
00:47:29,870 --> 00:47:32,430
我好久没看到这么漂亮的马路了
I haven't seen a road like this in years.

688
00:47:32,500 --> 00:47:36,630
- 我们走走吧，宝贝\n- 慢慢开
- Well, then let's cruise, baby. - Low and slow.

689
00:47:36,710 --> 00:47:38,900
[意大利语]天啊，真漂亮！
[Italian] E bellissima! It's beautiful!

690
00:47:38,980 --> 00:47:42,710
好像是天使们铺的路
Guido, look, it's-a like it was paved by angels.

691
00:47:43,650 --> 00:47:44,950
孩子们，我告诉你们
Boy, I tell you what.

692
00:47:45,020 --> 00:47:47,850
我打赌月亮上的路都没有这条平坦
I bet even the roads on the moon ain't this smooth.

693
00:47:47,920 --> 00:47:49,580
韩大夫，来看啊
Doc, look at this!

694
00:47:49,720 --> 00:47:52,590
早该判他修路了吧？
Shoulda tossed him into the cactus a lot sooner, huh?

695
00:47:52,660 --> 00:47:56,150
嗯，还早呢\n还有很长一段路没完成
Well, he ain't finished yet. Still got a long way to go.

696
00:47:56,230 --> 00:47:59,200
看看路易奇
Guido, look at Luigi!

697
00:47:59,800 --> 00:48:01,530
看起来太棒了
This is fantastico!

698
00:48:01,600 --> 00:48:05,060
很好玩的样子\n拖线，换我玩啦
That looks like fun! Mater, I got dibs, next turn!

699
00:48:05,140 --> 00:48:09,440
喂，路易奇，这条新路\n让你的店看起来像垃圾场
Hey, Luigi, this new road makes your place look like a dump.

700
00:48:10,110 --> 00:48:12,810
哼，那疯婆子
That crazy old devil woman.

701
00:48:13,280 --> 00:48:16,680
喔！
Oh!

702
00:48:16,750 --> 00:48:18,580
她说的对！
She's right!

703
00:48:18,650 --> 00:48:20,210
- 啊！\n- 戈里多！
- Ah! - Guido!

704
00:48:20,290 --> 00:48:24,050
哈，那小子干得不错啊
Huh. That punk actually did a good job.

705
00:48:25,320 --> 00:48:29,120
不过，他跑哪去啦？
Well, now... where the heck is he?

706
00:48:35,470 --> 00:48:38,200
警长，他又想偷溜了吗？
Sheriff! Is he makin' another run for it?

707
00:48:38,270 --> 00:48:41,640
不不不，他做到半夜时柏油用完了
No, no. He ran outta asphalt in the middle of the night,

708
00:48:41,710 --> 00:48:44,070
他问我能不能出来这里
and asked me if he could come down here.

709
00:48:44,140 --> 00:48:46,540
他想要再试过那个弯
All he's tryin' to do is make that there turn.

710
00:48:46,610 --> 00:48:49,450
不不不，哇呀
No, no, no, no! Oh, great.

711
00:48:49,920 --> 00:48:52,440
我一直试图在弯道跑出完美的弧线
Perfect turns on every track I've ever raced on.

712
00:48:54,650 --> 00:48:58,610
警长，你要不要去芙蓉那喝杯汽油
Sheriff, why don't you go get yourself a quart of oil at Flo's.

713
00:48:58,690 --> 00:49:00,090
我帮你看着他
I'll keep an eye on him.

714
00:49:00,160 --> 00:49:04,060
谢了，韩大夫\n我正觉得有点口渴
Well, thanks, Doc. I've been feelin' a quart low.

715
00:49:18,440 --> 00:49:20,910
这不是柏油路，这是泥路
This ain't asphalt, son. This is dirt.

716
00:49:20,980 --> 00:49:23,710
唉，你又想要干嘛\n你是来炫耀的吗？
Oh, great. What do you want? You here to gloat?

717
00:49:23,780 --> 00:49:27,120
在泥地里煞车没用\n你不能踩煞车
You don't have three-wheel brakes, so you got to pitch it hard,

718
00:49:27,190 --> 00:49:30,680
你得用油门来控制\n过弯时记得放油门
break it loose and then just drive it with the throttle.

719
00:49:30,760 --> 00:49:33,820
如果你开太快的话就会滑出去
Give it too much, you'll be outta the dirt and into the tulips.

720
00:49:33,890 --> 00:49:36,990
原来你不只是法官，还是个赛车高手
So you're a judge, a doctor and a racing expert.

721
00:49:37,060 --> 00:49:38,720
我简单说吧
I'll put it simple.

722
00:49:38,800 --> 00:49:42,960
如果你用力左转的话\n你会发现你开始往右转
If you're goin' hard enough left, you'll find yourself turnin' right.

723
00:49:44,040 --> 00:49:49,440
是吗，那可真有意思\n向右转却可以向左开，谢谢！
Oh... Right. That makes perfect sense. Turn right to go left! Yes! Thank you!

724
00:49:49,510 --> 00:49:51,310
或者我应该说，不，谢谢！
Or should I say, "No, thank you"?

725
00:49:51,380 --> 00:49:54,970
因为在一个相反的世界里\n那就代表谢谢你
Because in Opposite World, maybe that really means, "Thank you"!

726
00:49:57,780 --> 00:50:01,180
脑子有问题的老爷车
Crazy grandpa car. What an idiot!

727
00:50:08,830 --> 00:50:10,760
向右转却可以向左开
Turn right to go left.

728
00:50:12,030 --> 00:50:14,020
呃...
Hmm...

729
00:50:14,100 --> 00:50:15,160
哇！
Whoa!

730
00:50:16,540 --> 00:50:18,970
啊！
Oh!

731
00:50:19,440 --> 00:50:23,400
啊！这是...
- Ow! Oh, that...

732
00:50:24,980 --> 00:50:28,340
啊！
Ow!

733
00:50:29,780 --> 00:50:33,050
向右转却可以向左开，我试过了
Turn right to go left. Guess what. I tried it.

734
00:50:33,120 --> 00:50:36,210
神奇的事发生了，我向右开了！
You know what? This crazy thing happened... I went right!

735
00:50:36,290 --> 00:50:39,690
如果你总是自言自语\n人们会以为你是个疯子
You keep talkin' to yourself, people'll think you're crazy.

736
00:50:39,760 --> 00:50:43,690
- 谢谢你的提醒\n- 什么，我没在同你说话
- Thanks for the tip. - What? I wasn't talkin' to you!

737
00:50:50,570 --> 00:50:54,130
- [意大利语]\n- [意大利语]
- Oh, Guido, e bellissimo! - Che cosa?

738
00:50:54,210 --> 00:50:58,580
- 看上去太棒了！太棒了！\n- [意大利语]
- It looks great! This is great! - Ti piace, eh? Si, si, bellissimo.

739
00:51:01,180 --> 00:51:03,170
哦，天啊！
Oh, Lord.

740
00:51:03,250 --> 00:51:04,880
拖线！
Mater!

741
00:51:04,950 --> 00:51:07,110
我想让你今晚看管那个囚犯
I need you to watch the prisoner tonight.

742
00:51:07,190 --> 00:51:10,480
没问题，如果他又想逃跑怎么办？
Well, dad-gum! Wait a minute. What if he tries to run again?

743
00:51:10,560 --> 00:51:13,390
那就让他跑到没油\n再把他拖回来
Just let him run outta gas and tow him on back.

744
00:51:13,460 --> 00:51:15,930
- 你一定要一只眼睛紧紧盯住他\n- 是，长官
- But keep an eye on him. - Yes, sir!

745
00:51:17,030 --> 00:51:18,690
呃...
Oh...

746
00:51:18,760 --> 00:51:21,430
我被困在这里修这条破路
While I'm stuck here paving this stinkin' road,

747
00:51:21,500 --> 00:51:24,060
“路霸”却在加州争取加入迪纳哥
Chick's in California schmoozing Dinoco.

748
00:51:24,140 --> 00:51:27,400
我的迪纳哥！哇哇哇\n谁在碰我？
My Dinoco. Whoa, whoa, whoa! Who's touching me?

749
00:51:27,470 --> 00:51:29,770
路易奇正在给你修理
You have a slow leak. Guido, he fix.

750
00:51:29,840 --> 00:51:31,870
你铺了这么好的一条路
You make-a such a nice new road.

751
00:51:31,940 --> 00:51:34,610
如果你光顾我的店铺\n路易奇会好好招待你的
You come to my shop. Luigi take-a good care of you.

752
00:51:34,680 --> 00:51:36,270
尽管你不是一辆法拉利
Even though you not a Ferrari.

753
00:51:36,350 --> 00:51:40,440
如果你买四个轮胎\n我就给你免费全身修理
You buy four tires, I give you a full-a size spare

754
00:51:40,520 --> 00:51:44,390
- 全部免费！\n- 瞧，我所用的所有轮胎都是免费的
- absolutely free! - Look, I get all my tires for free.

755
00:51:44,460 --> 00:51:47,980
我喜欢你的作风，嘿
I like your style, eh?

756
00:51:48,060 --> 00:51:51,620
你喜欢讲价，好吧\n路易奇给你提供新的套餐
You drive the hard bargain. OK. Luigi make you a new deal.

757
00:51:51,700 --> 00:51:55,160
买一送三怎么样？
You buy one tire, I give you three for free!

758
00:51:55,230 --> 00:51:56,890
你觉得怎么样？
Oh, would you look at that?

759
00:51:56,970 --> 00:51:59,100
雷蒙，雷蒙
Ramone, Ramone!

760
00:51:59,170 --> 00:52:01,260
路易奇再和你谈笔买卖
Then Luigi make you a new new deal.

761
00:52:01,340 --> 00:52:04,330
不不不不，没有买卖，谢谢你
No, no, no, no. Deal me out. Pass. No, thank you.

762
00:52:04,410 --> 00:52:08,040
- 不不不不不\n- 好吧，我最后的报价
- No, no, no, no. No. - This is it. My last offer.

763
00:52:08,110 --> 00:52:12,810
买一送七！七个雪地防滑胎！
You buy one tire, I give you seven-a snow tires for free!

764
00:52:12,880 --> 00:52:15,750
如果你有兴趣就来找我\n你知道我在哪里
Done. You interested, you call me. You know where I am.

765
00:52:17,160 --> 00:52:18,320
啊！
Ah!

766
00:52:18,390 --> 00:52:20,520
停下！让我...
Stop! Let me...

767
00:52:21,930 --> 00:52:24,760
小红，你漏了一个地方\n这儿，看到了吗
Oh, Red, you missed a spot. See it right there?

768
00:52:24,830 --> 00:52:26,860
- 不！不！\n- 就在车前盖那里
- No! No! - On the hood right there.

769
00:52:26,930 --> 00:52:30,270
停！停下！冷死人了
Stop, stop! That's cold!

770
00:52:30,340 --> 00:52:32,830
快停下吧
Help! Please! Stop!

771
00:52:32,900 --> 00:52:36,270
谢谢你，小红
Thanks, Red.

772
00:52:37,510 --> 00:52:38,770
你为什么这么对我？
What was that for?

773
00:52:38,840 --> 00:52:40,970
- 你到底想不想住在舒适小锥里？\n- 嗯？
- Do you want to stay at the Cozy Cone? - Huh?

774
00:52:41,050 --> 00:52:42,540
如果你想，你必须洗干净
If you do, you gotta be clean.

775
00:52:42,610 --> 00:52:45,140
就算在这农村人的地方\n我们也有我们的准则
'Cause even in hillbilly hell we have standards.

776
00:52:45,220 --> 00:52:46,950
什么？我...我不明白
What, I...? I don't get it.

777
00:52:47,020 --> 00:52:49,610
我只是想感谢你所做的一切
I thought I'd say thank you for doin' a great job.

778
00:52:49,690 --> 00:52:52,920
所以我想让你和我住在一起\n不，不是和我在一起
So I thought I'd let you stay with me. I mean, not with me!

779
00:52:52,990 --> 00:52:57,620
是在那边，不是和我住在一个房间\n你住在你的房间
But there. Not with me there, but there in your own cozy cone.

780
00:52:57,700 --> 00:53:01,560
- 我住在我的房间\n- 等一等，你现在对我这么好
- And I'd be in my cone, and it's... - Wait. Wait, you're being nice to me.

781
00:53:01,630 --> 00:53:04,030
如果你想呆在肮脏的拘留所里，没问题
