01:05:14,130 --> 01:05:15,860
你是最棒的哈德逊大黄蜂！
You're The Fabulous Hudson Hornet!

945
01:05:15,930 --> 01:05:19,590
你还保持着一个赛季\n最多胜利场数的纪录，我们得谈谈
You used to hold the record for most wins in a season. Oh, we gotta talk.

946
01:05:19,670 --> 01:05:22,400
- 你一定要告诉我你的技巧\n- 我已经告诉过你了
- You gotta show me your tricks. Please. - I tried that.

947
01:05:22,470 --> 01:05:25,200
你赢过三次冠军，看看那些奖杯
You won three times! Look at those trophies!

948
01:05:25,270 --> 01:05:28,710
你看，我只看到一些没用的杯子
You look. All I see is a bunch of empty cups.

949
01:05:33,950 --> 01:05:39,250
做一些汽车瑜珈可以降低你的转速
You know, some automotive yoga could really lower your RPM's, man.

950
01:05:39,320 --> 01:05:41,120
去洗一下车吧，嬉皮士
Oh, take a car wash, hippie.

951
01:05:41,190 --> 01:05:44,420
大家快看我的丈夫\n哇！你是什么颜色？
Yeah, look at my husband, y'all! Whoo! That's your color!

952
01:05:44,490 --> 01:05:48,220
- 黄色，亲爱的\n- 你看上去真性感
- Yellow, baby. - Mmm. You smokin' hot!

953
01:05:48,300 --> 01:05:49,360
他来了
There he is.

954
01:05:49,430 --> 01:05:52,420
天啊，你们知不知道韩大夫\n是一辆有名的赛车？
Oh, my gosh! Did you know Doc is a famous racecar?

955
01:05:55,670 --> 01:05:58,440
- 韩大夫？我们的韩大夫？\n- 不是哈德逊大黄蜂吧？
- Doc? Our Doc? - Not Doc Hudson.

956
01:05:58,510 --> 01:06:01,100
不，那是真的！\n他是真正的赛车史上的传奇人物
No, no, no, no, it's true! He's a real racing legend.

957
01:06:01,180 --> 01:06:03,440
他是最棒的哈德逊大黄蜂！
He's The Fabulous Hudson Hornet!

958
01:06:03,510 --> 01:06:06,810
最棒的？我从没见过他时速超过20英里
Fabulous? I never seen Doc drive more than 20 miles an hour.

959
01:06:06,880 --> 01:06:08,940
你真正见过他参加比赛吗？
I mean, have you ever seen him race?

960
01:06:09,020 --> 01:06:12,610
没有，但是我真希望我可以见到\n他们说那真是棒极了
No, but I wish I could have. They say he was amazing!

961
01:06:12,690 --> 01:06:16,560
- 他赢了三个活塞杯\n- 他在他的杯里干了什么？
- He won three Piston Cups! - He did what in his cup?

962
01:06:16,630 --> 01:06:18,960
我想这个年轻人一定是快热昏头了
I think the heat's startin' to get to the boy!

963
01:06:19,030 --> 01:06:21,160
我想他已经热昏头了
Well, I'll say! Look how red he is.

964
01:06:21,230 --> 01:06:23,630
他的玻璃需要镀膜了
I think he needs a new coat of poly, man.

965
01:06:23,700 --> 01:06:26,460
- 你病了吗，伙计？\n- 的确有点像
-  Are you sick, buddy? - You are lookin' peaked.

966
01:06:26,540 --> 01:06:28,300
他的玻璃需要镀膜了！
He needs a new coat of poly for sure!

967
01:06:30,610 --> 01:06:34,130
- 嘿！你干什么？\n- 没关系，你相信我，对不对？
- Hey! What are you doin'? - It's OK. You can trust me, right?

968
01:06:34,210 --> 01:06:36,910
我当然相信你，我担心的是他
I trust you, all right. It's him I'm worried about.

969
01:06:37,850 --> 01:06:40,180
我相信他
Hmm... I trust him.

970
01:06:41,150 --> 01:06:43,450
- 我们去兜兜风\n- 兜风？
- Come on, let's take a drive. - A drive?

971
01:06:43,520 --> 01:06:44,820
没错，兜风
Yeah, a drive.

972
01:06:44,890 --> 01:06:48,020
像你这样大城市里的赛车\n从来没有兜过风吗？
Don't you big city racecars ever just take a drive?

973
01:06:48,090 --> 01:06:50,790
呃...没有，从来没有
Ah... No. No, we don't.

974
01:07:13,280 --> 01:07:17,120
你到底来不来？
Hey, Stickers! You comin' or what?

975
01:07:22,930 --> 01:07:24,120
嗯
Mm-hm!

976
01:07:24,190 --> 01:07:27,650
- 你还以为他要逃跑\n- 嘿，你相信吗？
- And you thought he was gonna run. - Hey, can you believe it, man?

977
01:07:27,730 --> 01:07:30,160
他以为韩大夫是一辆有名的赛车
He actually thought Doc was a famous racecar!

978
01:07:31,200 --> 01:07:33,170
真是想的太多了！
That's so too much!

979
01:07:35,200 --> 01:07:37,670
我们出来了，我们要去哪里？
OK, you got me out here. Where are we goin'?

980
01:07:37,740 --> 01:07:39,730
我也不知道
I don't know.

981
01:07:44,610 --> 01:07:46,600
哇！耶
Whoa! Yes.

982
01:08:03,430 --> 01:08:05,060
哦！哈哈！
Oh! Ah-ha-ha!

983
01:08:05,130 --> 01:08:08,800
啊！
Bleah!

984
01:09:12,740 --> 01:09:14,790
哦！
Oh!

985
01:09:35,060 --> 01:09:38,790
这是什么地方？
Wow. What is this place?

986
01:09:39,500 --> 01:09:40,860
中转中心
Wheel Well.

987
01:09:40,930 --> 01:09:44,190
以前是公路旁最热闹的落脚点
Used to be the most popular stop on the mother road.

988
01:09:48,840 --> 01:09:50,570
这个地方？
This place?

989
01:09:54,180 --> 01:09:56,240
是啊，真是很难想像
Yeah, imagine.

990
01:09:57,910 --> 01:10:00,640
想像呆在这里是什么感觉
Oh, imagine what it must have been like to stay here.

991
01:10:02,990 --> 01:10:04,540
我好像不是很了解你
You know, I don't get you.

992
01:10:04,620 --> 01:10:07,850
一辆保时捷怎么会呆在这个地方？
How does a Porsche wind up in a place like this?

993
01:10:07,920 --> 01:10:10,120
其实很简单，我从前
Well, it's really pretty simple. I was...

994
01:10:10,190 --> 01:10:14,360
我在洛杉矶是一个律师\n生活节奏是那么的快
...an attorney in LA livin' life in the fast lane, and...

995
01:10:14,430 --> 01:10:17,990
是吗？你很富有吗？
Oh, you were, were you? Were you rich?

996
01:10:18,070 --> 01:10:21,470
- 什么？\n- 只是想知道答案
- What? - Just... clues to the puzzle.

997
01:10:22,240 --> 01:10:24,870
是的，我的生活是这样的
Yeah, OK. Well, that was my life.

998
01:10:24,940 --> 01:10:26,700
你知道吗？
And you know what?

999
01:10:26,780 --> 01:10:30,400
我从未感到开心过
It never felt... happy.

1000
01:10:32,050 --> 01:10:35,140
真的吗？
Yeah. I mean... really?

1001
01:10:35,220 --> 01:10:36,950
最后我离开了加州
Yeah. So I left California.

1002
01:10:37,020 --> 01:10:40,320
一直开啊开，最后终于坏在了这里
Just drove and drove and finally broke down right here.

1003
01:10:41,060 --> 01:10:43,850
韩大夫把我修好，芙蓉收留了我
Doc fixed me up, Flo took me in.

1004
01:10:43,930 --> 01:10:46,920
他们都收留了我，我再也没有离开过
Well, they all did. And I never left.

1005
01:10:48,200 --> 01:10:49,890
我理解你
Yeah. You know, I understand.

1006
01:10:49,970 --> 01:10:52,800
需要放松一下，给你的电池充充电
You need a little R and R. Recharge the old batteries.

1007
01:10:52,870 --> 01:10:56,600
但是过了这么长时间\n你为什么不回去
But you know, after a while, why didn't you go back?

1008
01:10:57,570 --> 01:11:01,030
我坠入了爱河
I fell in love.

1009
01:11:01,110 --> 01:11:04,770
- 哦\n- 没错
- Oh. - Yep.

1010
01:11:05,610 --> 01:11:08,410
- 雪佛兰？\n- 不是
- Corvette? - No.

1011
01:11:13,960 --> 01:11:16,720
我爱上这里的景色了
I fell in love with this.

1012
01:11:28,740 --> 01:11:32,470
哇，快看啊
Whoa. Look at that.

1013
01:11:33,340 --> 01:11:35,670
他们只是驶过这里
Look, they're drivin' right by.

1014
01:11:35,740 --> 01:11:37,940
他们都不知道他们错过了什么
They don't even know what they're missing!

1015
01:11:38,950 --> 01:11:41,280
以前并不是这样的
Well, it didn't used to be that way.

1016
01:11:42,750 --> 01:11:44,080
是吗？
Oh, yeah?

1017
01:11:44,150 --> 01:11:48,060
没错，40年前，那条州际公路并不存在
Yeah. Forty years ago, that Interstate down there didn't exist.

1018
01:11:49,190 --> 01:11:50,180
真的吗？
Really?

1019
01:11:50,260 --> 01:11:52,960
是的，以前
Yeah. Back then,

1020
01:11:53,030 --> 01:11:55,900
车在州之间穿行的方法\n和现在是完全不同的
cars came across the country a whole different way.

1021
01:11:57,170 --> 01:11:58,500
你是什么意思？
How do you mean?

1022
01:11:58,570 --> 01:12:01,970
路并不像那条州际公路一样\n直接穿过沙漠
The road didn't cut through the land like that Interstate.

1023
01:12:02,040 --> 01:12:06,240
路是根据地形曲折蜿蜒的
It moved with the land, you know? It rose, it fell, it curved.

1024
01:12:07,740 --> 01:12:09,730
- 早上好！\n- 天气真不错
- Mornin'! - Nice day, huh?

1025
01:12:11,650 --> 01:12:14,450
车不是为了使自己高兴而驾驶
Cars didn't drive on it to make great time.

1026
01:12:14,520 --> 01:12:17,080
他们是为了享受这个美好时光而驾驶
They drove on it to have a great time.

1027
01:12:51,090 --> 01:12:53,490
然后发生了什么？
Well, what happened?

1028
01:12:53,560 --> 01:12:57,010
为了节省10分钟的驾驶时间\n公路饶过了我们这里
The town got bypassed just to save ten minutes of driving.

1029
01:14:23,180 --> 01:14:26,770
能看到这城镇的昌盛时期该有多好
How great would it have been to see this place in its heyday!

1030
01:14:26,850 --> 01:14:29,650
我都不知梦想过多少次了
Oh, I can't tell you how many times I've dreamed of that.

1031
01:14:29,720 --> 01:14:33,380
终有一天我们会让它回到地图上
But one of these days we'll find a way to get it back on the map.

1032
01:14:33,460 --> 01:14:37,120
是啊，嘿，谢谢你带我兜风
Yeah. Hey, listen, thanks for the drive.

1033
01:14:37,190 --> 01:14:39,020
我感到很高兴
I had a great time.

1034
01:14:39,090 --> 01:14:41,820
有时慢慢开感觉还不错
It's kinda nice to slow down every once in a while.

1035
01:14:42,460 --> 01:14:44,630
不用谢
You're welcome.

1036
01:14:52,010 --> 01:14:53,270
听着
Hey, listen, listen!

1037
01:14:53,340 --> 01:14:56,440
如果有人问起我们\n就说我们去撞信箱了
If anybody asks you, we was out smashin' mailboxes, OK?

1038
01:14:56,510 --> 01:14:58,600
什么？
Wha... what?

1039
01:15:13,930 --> 01:15:15,990
哦，漆还没有干呢
Oh, man, the paint's still wet!

1040
01:15:26,610 --> 01:15:28,470
不不不，离开我的店铺
No, no, no, no! Get out of the store!

1041
01:15:28,540 --> 01:15:32,140
不要吃我的轮胎，吃这些旧的轮胎
Hey! Don't eat the radial! Here, take-a the snow tires.

1042
01:15:32,210 --> 01:15:34,510
- 拖线\n- 你可有麻烦了
- Mater! - I wasn't tractor-tippin'!

1043
01:15:34,580 --> 01:15:37,610
这些拖拉机是从哪里来的？
Then where did all these gol-durn tractors come from?

1044
01:15:37,850 --> 01:15:40,190
- 嘿，伙计\n- 嘿！嘿！伙计
- Whoa, boy! - Hey! Hey, guys!

1045
01:15:40,260 --> 01:15:42,220
有一个向那边去了
There's one goin' this way.

1046
01:15:43,190 --> 01:15:45,390
我去追他
I got it.

1047
01:15:48,900 --> 01:15:51,200
快过来，小拖拉机，快过来
Come here, little tractor, come here.

1048
01:15:51,270 --> 01:15:53,530
真是个乖拖拉机
Yeah, that's a good tractor.

1049
01:15:53,600 --> 01:15:54,970
不不不不，过来这里
No, no, no, no, come here.

1050
01:15:55,040 --> 01:15:56,400
你在干什么？
What are you doing?

1051
01:15:56,470 --> 01:15:59,170
你不应该在这里
You're not supposed to go wandering off all...

1052
01:15:59,470 --> 01:16:01,840
单独闲逛
...alone.

1053
01:16:12,220 --> 01:16:16,450
你想用这些老旧的赛车轮胎干什么？
What are you doin' with those old racin' tires?

1054
01:16:23,130 --> 01:16:25,430
来吧，韩大夫，跑吧
Come on, Doc, drive.

1055
01:17:43,310 --> 01:17:45,110
太棒了
Ah... Yeah.

1056
01:17:45,180 --> 01:17:46,840
- 哇！\n- 嗯？
- Wow. - Huh?

1057
01:17:46,920 --> 01:17:48,510
你真是太棒了
You're amazing!

1058
01:17:50,490 --> 01:17:52,750
你要去哪？
What are you doin'?

1059
01:17:52,820 --> 01:17:54,520
韩大夫，等一等
Doc, wait!

1060
01:17:58,390 --> 01:18:00,830
往这边走！快点，生锈的家伙们
Giddup right in there! Come on, Rusty.

1061
01:18:03,730 --> 01:18:06,930
韩大夫，你的技术真是太棒了！
Doc, hold it! Seriously, your driving's incredible!

1062
01:18:07,000 --> 01:18:10,300
- 太好了，现在请你离开\n- 我是认真的，你还是和以前一样棒
- Wonderful. Now, go away. - Hey, I mean it. You've still got it!

1063
01:18:10,370 --> 01:18:12,200
- 我叫你离开这里\n- 得了吧
- I'm askin' you to leave. - Come on.

1064
01:18:12,270 --> 01:18:15,270
我是一辆赛车\n你是一辆老式的赛车
I'm a racecar, you're a much older racecar,

1065
01:18:15,340 --> 01:18:17,330
但是在引擎盖下面，我们是一样的
but under the hood you and I are the same.

1066
01:18:17,410 --> 01:18:20,470
我们并不一样！\n明白了吗？现在离开这里
We are not the same! Understand? Now, get out.

1067
01:18:20,550 --> 01:18:23,480
一辆像你这样的车\n为什么在你的尖峰时期退出？
How could a car like you quit at the top of your game?

1068
01:18:25,350 --> 01:18:27,820
你以为我退出了？
You think I quit?

1069
01:18:40,400 --> 01:18:42,100
是啊
Right.

1070
01:18:42,740 --> 01:18:45,370
54年的大撞车
Your big wreck in '54.

1071
01:18:46,110 --> 01:18:48,410
他们离开了我
They quit on me.

1072
01:18:48,480 --> 01:18:52,040
当我完全修好后\n我回去以为别人会热烈欢迎我
When I finally got put together, I went back expecting a big welcome.

1073
01:18:52,110 --> 01:18:55,010
知道他们怎么说吗？\n你已经是历史了
You know what they said? "You're history."

1074
01:18:55,080 --> 01:18:58,140
他们挑选了一位新人
Moved right on to the next rookie standing in line.

1075
01:19:00,990 --> 01:19:03,220
我还有很多能量可以发挥
There was a lot left in me.

1076
01:19:03,960 --> 01:19:06,950
但是我却没有机会再表现了
I never got a chance to show 'em.

1077
01:19:08,460 --> 01:19:12,490
我把新闻留了下来
I keep that to remind me never to go back.

1078
01:19:13,670 --> 01:19:16,830
来提醒我永远不要回头了
I just never expected that that world would...

1079
01:19:16,910 --> 01:19:19,100
我没有预料到会有人找到我
...would find me here.

1080
01:19:20,210 --> 01:19:22,800
- 韩大夫，我可不像他们\n- 是吗？
- Hey, look, Doc, I'm not them. - Oh, yeah?

1081
01:19:22,880 --> 01:19:23,870
我不像他们
No, I'm not.

1082
01:19:23,950 --> 01:19:27,780
你最后一次关心除了你自己\n以外的人是什么时候？
When is the last time you cared about something except yourself, hot rod?

1083
01:19:27,850 --> 01:19:32,450
你说出一次来，我就回去参加比赛
You name me one time and I will take it all back.

1084
01:19:34,290 --> 01:19:37,280
呃...我可不这样认为
Uh-huh. I didn't think so.

1085
01:19:37,690 --> 01:19:41,460
这里的人都是好人\n每个人都关心对方
These are good folk around here, who care about one another.

1086
01:19:42,100 --> 01:19:45,230
我不想让他们依赖一个不值得依赖的人
I don't want 'em depending on someone they can't count on.

1087
01:19:45,800 --> 01:19:47,830
像你吗？\n你已经来这里多久了
Oh, like you? You've been here how long

1088
01:19:47,900 --> 01:19:50,130
你的朋友们都不知道你真正的身份？
and your friends don't even know who you are?

1089
01:19:50,810 --> 01:19:52,860
到底是谁只会关心自己？
Who's caring about only himself?

1090
01:19:52,940 --> 01:19:55,740
快点修完那条路，然后离开这里！
Just finish that road and get outta here!

1091
01:20:09,890 --> 01:20:12,590
你可不可以把那不尊重国旗音乐给关了
Will you turn that disrespectful junk off?

1092
01:20:12,660 --> 01:20:15,100
尊重古典音乐
Respect the classics, man.

1093
01:20:24,840 --> 01:20:27,640
啊
Ah...

1094
01:20:41,560 --> 01:20:42,920
他完成了
He's done.

1095
01:20:42,990 --> 01:20:46,220
他一定是在我们睡觉时完成的
He must've finished it while we was all sleepin'.

1096
01:20:46,290 --> 01:20:48,520
太好了
Good riddance.

1097
01:20:56,400 --> 01:20:57,840
他走了？
He's gone?

1098
01:20:57,910 --> 01:21:00,930
我们可不想让他错过那个比赛
Well, we wouldn't want him to miss that race of his.

1099
01:21:06,380 --> 01:21:10,720
- 伙计，你是在哭吗？\n- 不，我是太高兴了
- Oh, dude, are you crying? - No! I'm happy!

1100
01:21:10,790 --> 01:21:13,750
我不用每天再看着他了
I don't have to watch him every second of the day anymore!

1101
01:21:13,820 --> 01:21:15,020
他走了我很高兴
I'm glad he's gone!

1102
01:21:21,630 --> 01:21:23,430
小红，怎么了？
What's wrong with Red?

1103
01:21:23,500 --> 01:21:26,900
因为你走了，他感到很难过
Oh, he's just sad 'cause you left town

1104
01:21:26,970 --> 01:21:29,900
你去参加你的比赛
and went to your big race to win the Piston Cup

1105
01:21:29,970 --> 01:21:32,840
去赢取你梦寐以求的活塞杯
that you've always dreamed about your whole life

1106
01:21:32,910 --> 01:21:38,440
得到有钱的赞助商的赞助\n还有直升机接送
and get that big ol' sponsor and that fancy helicopter you was talkin' about.

1107
01:21:43,080 --> 01:21:45,380
等一下！
Wait a minute!

1108
01:21:46,790 --> 01:21:49,620
我知道你不会不说再见就离开的
I knowed you wouldn't leave without saying goodbye.

1109
01:21:49,690 --> 01:21:52,420
你还呆在这里干什么？\n你会错过你的比赛的
What are you doin' here? You're gonna miss your race.

1110
01:21:52,490 --> 01:21:56,160
没关系，我用警车护送你\n把失去的时间赢回来
Don't worry. I'll give you a police escort, and we'll make up time.

1111
01:21:56,230 --> 01:21:57,390
谢谢，警长
Thank you, Sheriff.

1112
01:21:57,470 --> 01:21:59,590
但是我现在还不能走
But you know I can't go just yet.

1113
01:21:59,670 --> 01:22:01,160
为什么？
Well, why not?

1114
01:22:01,240 --> 01:22:04,070
我想我的轮胎
- I'm not sure these tires...

1115
01:22:04,140 --> 01:22:07,040
- 没法熬到加州\n- 换胎吗？
...can get me to California. - Peet stop?

1116
01:22:07,110 --> 01:22:10,370
你们谁知道路易奇的店什么时候开门？
Yeah, does anybody know what time Luigi's opens?

1117
01:22:10,450 --> 01:22:11,780
我真是不敢相信！四个全新的轮胎
I can't-a believe it! Four new tires!

1118
01:22:11,780 --> 01:22:13,610
I can't-a believe it! Four new tires!

1119
01:22:13,820 --> 01:22:16,410
谢谢你，“闪电”麦坤
Grazie, Mr. Lightning. Grazie!

1120
01:22:16,480 --> 01:22:20,580
- 你看看！\n- 这几年来我的第一位顾客！
- Would you look at that! -  Our first customer in years!

1121
01:22:20,660 --> 01:22:24,250
我满含激动的泪水
I am filled with tears of ecstasy,

1122
01:22:24,330 --> 01:22:28,190
这是我生命中最快乐的一天
for this is the most glorious day of my life!

1123
01:22:28,260 --> 01:22:32,260
好了，路易奇，把你最好的黑轮胎给我
All right, Luigi, give me the best set of blackwalls you've got.

1124
01:22:32,470 --> 01:22:33,700
不！不不不
No! No, no, no.

1125
01:22:33,770 --> 01:22:37,140
你不知道你想要什么\n路易奇知道你想要什么
You don't-a know what you want. Luigi know what you want.

1126
01:22:38,270 --> 01:22:42,640
黑轮胎，太寻常了
Blackwall tires. They blend into the pavement.

1127
01:22:42,710 --> 01:22:44,180
但是这个
But-a this...

1128
01:22:44,480 --> 01:22:46,310
白色的轮胎！
Whitewall tires!

1129
01:22:46,380 --> 01:22:51,550
好像是在说，快看我！\n我在这，爱上我
They say, "Look at me! Here I am! Love me."

1130
01:22:51,620 --> 01:22:53,420
好吧，你是专家
All right, you're the expert.

1131
01:22:53,490 --> 01:22:56,420
别忘了备用胎
Don't forget the spare.

1132
01:22:56,490 --> 01:22:59,320
- 太棒了，奇诺\n- 开工！
- Perfetto. Guido! - Peet stop!

1133
01:23:10,710 --> 01:23:13,640
我是怎么跟你说的，嗯？
What did Luigi tell you, eh?

1134
01:23:13,710 --> 01:23:17,170
你说的对极了\n比法拉利还要漂亮，对吗？
Wow, you were right. Better than a Ferrari, huh?

1135
01:23:17,950 --> 01:23:19,110
呃...不对
Eh... No.

1136
01:23:22,980 --> 01:23:26,580
这个有机汽油真是在棒了\n我以前怎么没听说过
Wow! This organic fuel is great! Why haven't I heard about it before?

1137
01:23:26,650 --> 01:23:28,650
这是一个阴谋！
It's a conspiracy, man!

1138
01:23:28,720 --> 01:23:31,190
那些公司和政府有交易！
The oil companies got a grip on the government!

1139
01:23:31,260 --> 01:23:34,490
他们告诉我们的都是谎话
They're feedin' us a bunch of lies, man.

1140
01:23:34,560 --> 01:23:36,690
好的，给我来一桶
OK, I'll take a case.

1141
01:23:51,750 --> 01:23:53,210
哦！额
Ow! Eh!

1142
01:24:02,060 --> 01:24:03,680
啊，耶
Ah... Yeah.

1143
01:24:04,230 --> 01:24:05,750
咔嚓
Ka-chow.

1144
01:24:06,630 --> 01:24:09,600
- 她来了！\n- 让路，伙计们，快
- Here she comes! - Places, everybody. Hurry!

1145
01:24:09,660 --> 01:24:11,390
自然一点
- Act natural.

1146
01:24:11,470 --> 01:24:12,800
嗨，莎莉
- Hi, Sally. - Buon giorno!

1147
01:24:12,870 --> 01:24:14,700
好了，到底怎么回事？
All right, what's goin' on?

1148
01:24:14,770 --> 01:24:16,930
女士们先生们
Ladies and gentlecars,

1149
01:24:17,010 --> 01:24:20,940
请欢迎崭新的“闪电”麦坤！
please welcome the new Lightning McQueen!

1150
01:24:21,580 --> 01:24:23,570
你认为怎么样？
Pow! What do you think?

1151
01:24:23,650 --> 01:24:25,840
水乡温泉镇\n这漆在我身上看起来不错
Radiator Springs looks pretty good on me.

1152
01:24:25,910 --> 01:24:27,710
我说
I'll say.

1153
01:24:27,780 --> 01:24:30,980
咔嚓
Ka-chow.

1154
01:24:31,050 --> 01:24:33,580
你一定很适合加州
You're gonna fit right in in California.

1155
01:24:34,460 --> 01:24:37,580
天啊，你帮助了城镇里的每一个人
My goodness. It looks like you've helped everybody in town.

1156
01:24:37,660 --> 01:24:39,490
耶，除了一个人
Yeah, everybody except one.

1157
01:24:40,730 --> 01:24:45,720
- 现在是不是天黑了？\n- 什么？他说什么？
- Hey, is it getting dark out? - What? What'd he say?

1158
01:24:45,800 --> 01:24:48,830
我再说一次\n现在是不是天黑了？
Let me say that again. Is it getting dark out?

1159
01:24:48,900 --> 01:24:51,100
我应该做什么？
Now, what was I supposed to do after that?

1160
01:25:15,100 --> 01:25:17,890
他们修好了霓虹灯
They fixed their neon!

1161
01:25:25,310 --> 01:25:30,300
- 低一些慢一些\n- 好的，亲爱的
- Low and slow? - Oh, yeah, baby!

1162
01:25:34,620 --> 01:25:37,950
就像这个城镇的昌盛时期，对吗？
Just like in its heyday, right?

1163
01:25:38,020 --> 01:25:41,390
比我想像中的还要好，谢谢你
It's even better than I pictured it. Thank you.

1164
01:26:08,820 --> 01:26:10,250
我们要去兜风吗？
Shall we cruise?

1165
01:26:10,320 --> 01:26:12,650
谢谢你，亲爱的，我非常想去
Oh, thank you, dear. I'd love to!

1166
01:26:12,720 --> 01:26:14,190
- 不不不！\n- 莉奇
- No, no, no. - Lizzie!

1167
01:26:14,260 --> 01:26:18,590
我还记的斯坦利第一次叫我和他去兜风
I remember when Stanley first asked me to take a drive with him.

1168
01:26:18,660 --> 01:26:21,530
你好，莎莉，我可以请你去兜风吗？
Hey, Miss Sally. May I have this cruise?

1169
01:26:21,600 --> 01:26:24,960
- 当然可以，拖线\n- 呃！
- Of course, Mater. - Uh-uh-uh!

1170
01:26:31,440 --> 01:26:35,810
我一次一次说不\n他又问了我一次，我还是说不去
...and again and I said, "No." He asked me again, and I said, "No."

1171
01:26:35,880 --> 01:26:40,210
对于一个2缸的车来说，他真是太漂亮了
But, oh, he was a persistent little bugger for a two-cylinder.

1172
01:26:40,280 --> 01:26:43,680
最后我说，只能兜一会儿
Finally I said, "All right, one little drive."

1173
01:26:45,850 --> 01:26:48,850
哦！
- Oh!

1174
01:26:53,190 --> 01:26:55,320
- 嘿！\n- 谢谢，拖线
- Hey! - Thanks, Mater.

1175
01:26:55,400 --> 01:26:57,690
你们两个晚安
Good evenin', you two.

1176
01:27:00,200 --> 01:27:05,430
斯坦利，我真希望你可以看到这个景象
Oh, Stanley, I wish you could see this.

1177
01:27:09,540 --> 01:27:13,340
- 那是我想看到的吗？\n- 我不知道，芙蓉
- Is that what I think it is? - Oh, I don't know, Flo.

1178
01:27:13,410 --> 01:27:19,080
我还不知道结果是什么\n但是我会找出结果的
I haven't had a chance to find out. But I am going to find out. Hello.

1179
01:27:19,150 --> 01:27:21,750
不是那个
Not that. That.

1180
01:27:21,890 --> 01:27:24,220
顾客？\n顾客？
Customers?\nCustomers?

1181
01:27:24,290 --> 01:27:26,950
大伙，顾客们来了！有很多顾客
Customers, everybody! And a lot of 'em!

1182
01:27:27,030 --> 01:27:29,190
你们知道该怎么做了\n就像我们排练的一样
You know what to do. Just like we rehearsed.

1183
01:27:30,330 --> 01:27:32,930
那是幽灵之光！
It's the ghostlight!

1184
01:27:33,000 --> 01:27:35,590
我们找到了麦坤\n我们找到了麦坤！
We have found McQueen. We have found McQueen!

1185
01:27:36,470 --> 01:27:37,940
麦坤看这边
McQueen, over here!

1186
01:27:38,010 --> 01:27:40,770
- 等一等\n- 他们说你去戒毒所了
- Wait, excuse me. - Is it true you've been in rehab?

1187
01:27:40,840 --> 01:27:42,970
- 他们说你被压力压跨了？\n- 什么？
- Did you have a nervous breakdown? - What?

1188
01:27:43,040 --> 01:27:45,770
- 麦坤用上了白色的轮胎\n- 你的胎坏了吗？
- McQueen's wearing whitewalls! - Your tires balding?

1189
01:27:45,850 --> 01:27:46,840
麦坤
Stickers!

1190
01:27:46,910 --> 01:27:49,080
- 麦坤是不是你的囚犯？\n- 当然不是！
- Was McQueen your prisoner? - Shoot, no!

1191
01:27:49,150 --> 01:27:51,620
才不是呢，我们是最好的朋友
We're best buds! I ain't braggin' or nothin',

1192
01:27:51,690 --> 01:27:54,880
我只是在他逃跑时负责捉住他
but I was in charge of huntin' him down if he tried to escape.

1193
01:27:54,960 --> 01:27:56,550
莎莉！莎莉！
Sally! Sally!

1194
01:27:56,620 --> 01:27:58,680
你还会参加活塞杯吗？
Will you still race for the Piston Cup?

1195
01:27:58,760 --> 01:28:00,490
- 麦坤？\n- 莎莉！
- Stickers? - Sally!

1196
01:28:00,560 --> 01:28:02,960
看这边，闪一下！
- Come on, give us some bolt!

1197
01:28:03,030 --> 01:28:07,520
你在这里！感谢上帝，你还活着
You're here! Thank the manufacturer! You're alive!

1198
01:28:07,600 --> 01:28:10,970
- 麦大叔？\n- 我真不敢相信你在这里！
- Mack? - You're here! I can't believe it!

1199
01:28:11,040 --> 01:28:14,910
你是新闻头条！
You are a sight for sore headlights!

1200
01:28:14,980 --> 01:28:17,710
对不起我把你搞丢了，老板
I'm so sorry I lost you, boss. I'll make it up to you!

1201
01:28:17,780 --> 01:28:19,640
麦大叔，真不敢相信你在这儿
Mack, I, I can't believe you're here.

1202
01:28:19,710 --> 01:28:22,310
这不是世界上最快的赛车吗？
Is that the world's fastest racing machine?

1203
01:28:22,380 --> 01:28:24,910
- 那是哈夫吗？\n- 是的，哈夫就在后面
- Is that Harv? - Yeah. He's in the back.

1204
01:28:26,520 --> 01:28:29,460
- 秀一下闪电！\n- 退后，狗仔队
- Show us the bolt! - Get back, you oil-thirsty parasites!

1205
01:28:29,520 --> 01:28:32,790
- 老麦坤在哪里？\n- 实际上这是我好的一面
- Where's the old McQueen? - Actually, this is my good side here.

1206
01:28:33,090 --> 01:28:35,120
- 哈夫！哈夫！\n- 秀下下闪电！
- Harv! Harv! - Give us the bolt!

1207
01:28:36,060 --> 01:28:37,050
- 哈夫？\n- 我在这里！
- Harv? - Come on!

1208
01:28:37,130 --> 01:28:39,830
- 小子，我在这儿\n- 你还好吗，伙计
- Kid, I'm over here! - How you doin', buddy?

1209
01:28:39,900 --> 01:28:42,560
我的明星客户从地球上消失了！
My star client disappears off the face of the earth!

1210
01:28:42,640 --> 01:28:44,830
- 你说我感觉如何？\n- 我可以解释
- How do you think I'm doing? - I can explain.

1211
01:28:44,910 --> 01:28:49,310
我感觉好极了！你在各种媒体上\n电视，广播，报纸
I'm doing great! You're everywhere! Radio, TV, the papers!

1212
01:28:49,380 --> 01:28:52,440
这是用钱也买不到的暴光率！\n你还要我干什么
You can't buy this kind of publicity! What do you need me for?

1213
01:28:52,510 --> 01:28:54,980
那只是些客套话，因为你签了合约
That's just a figure of speech, by the way. You signed a contract.

1214
01:28:55,050 --> 01:28:57,350
你在哪里？我在我个导航仪上找不到你
Where are you? I can't even find you on my GPS.

1215
01:28:57,420 --> 01:28:59,940
我在一个叫水乡温泉镇的地方
I'm in this little town called Radiator Springs.

1216
01:29:00,050 --> 01:29:03,220
- 你知道66号州际公路吗？它就在这里！\n- 很好，太棒了，孩子
- You know Route 66? It's still here! - Yeah, that's great, kid.

1217
01:29:03,290 --> 01:29:04,490
游戏结束了
Playtime is over, pal.

1218
01:29:04,560 --> 01:29:08,390
当整个世界都在找你的时候\n迪纳哥没有人可以选择
While the world's been trying to find you Dinoco has had no one to woo.

1219
01:29:08,460 --> 01:29:10,160
- 他们要选择谁？\n- 路霸！
- Who are they gonna woo? - Chick!

1220
01:29:10,230 --> 01:29:13,860
没错，看看电视上在播什么
Bingo. In fact, check out what's on the plasma right now.

1221
01:29:13,940 --> 01:29:16,100
- 给我看看雷鸣！\n- 你要看雷鸣？
- Show us the thunder! - You want thunder?

1222
01:29:16,170 --> 01:29:19,800
要看雷鸣？咔嚓，咔嚓
You want thunder? Ka-chicka, ka-chicka!

1223
01:29:19,870 --> 01:29:23,140
- 嘿，那是我的招牌动作！\n- 你现在要马上赶到那里！
- Hey, that's my bit! - You've gotta get to Cali, pronto!

1224
01:29:23,210 --> 01:29:27,200
马上离开水乡温泉镇，不然你永远没有机会\n和迪纳哥合作了，知道吗？
Just get out of Radiation Stinks now, or Dinoco is history, you hear me?

1225
01:29:27,280 --> 01:29:29,010
等一下，哈夫
Just give me a second here, Harv.

1226
01:29:29,180 --> 01:29:30,880
不行，等等，你去哪里？
No, wait. Where are you goin'?

1227
01:29:30,950 --> 01:29:34,220
进拖车吧，孩子，想要个更大一点的拖车吗？
Get in the trailer, baby. Kid! You want a bigger trailer?

1228
01:29:38,360 --> 01:29:41,160
莎莉，我想让你知道
Sally, I... I want you to...

1229
01:29:41,800 --> 01:29:44,890
瞧，我想
Look, I wish...

1230
01:29:46,370 --> 01:29:49,230
谢谢，谢谢你所做的一切
Thank you. Thanks for everything.

1231
01:29:51,410 --> 01:29:56,600
- 只是修了一条路而已\n- 不，不只是一条路而已
- It was just a road. - No. It was much more than that.

1232
01:29:59,750 --> 01:30:02,940
嘿，小子，我们该走了\n哈夫快疯了
Hey, kid! We gotta go. Harv's goin' crazy!

1233
01:30:03,020 --> 01:30:06,250
如果你现在不进到卡车里\n他会解雇我的！
He's gonna have me fired if I don't get you in the truck right now!

1234
01:30:06,320 --> 01:30:09,050
- 麦大叔，再等一会\n- 该走了
- Mack, just... hold it for... - You should go.

1235
01:30:09,120 --> 01:30:11,350
- 我知道，但是\n- 祝你好运
- I know, but... - Good luck in California.

1236
01:30:13,730 --> 01:30:16,750
我希望你可以找到你所期望的
I hope you find what you're looking for.

1237
01:30:16,830 --> 01:30:18,920
- 麦坤，快点！\n- 莎莉
- McQueen, come on! - Sally...

1238
01:30:19,000 --> 01:30:22,230
- 莎莉！\n- 秀一下闪电，麦坤，秀一下！
- Sally! - Show us the bolt, McQueen! The bolt!

1239
01:30:22,300 --> 01:30:24,400
嘿，“闪电”，秀一下
Hey, Lightning, show us the bolt!

1240
01:30:30,240 --> 01:30:33,010
- 快进来\n- 原来的麦坤呢？
- Come on, get in the trailer. - Where's the old McQueen?

1241
01:30:33,080 --> 01:30:35,450
- 闪光！\n- 很好，我们走了
- The bolt! - That's it. That's right, let's go!

1242
01:30:35,520 --> 01:30:38,210
你是巨星，超级巨星
You're a big shining star. You're a superstar.

1243
01:30:38,290 --> 01:30:40,580
你根本不属于这里
You don't belong there, anyway.

1244
01:30:40,660 --> 01:30:43,650
等，等等，等等！
Whoa... Wait... Whoa, whoa, wait, wait!

1245
01:30:46,460 --> 01:30:48,690
嘿，伙计们，他钻进卡车里了
Hey, guys! McQueen's leavin' in the truck!

1246
01:30:55,840 --> 01:30:58,200
嘿，你是韩大夫吗？
Hey, are you Doc Hudson?

1247
01:30:58,270 --> 01:31:00,670
- 是的\n- 谢谢你打电话来
- Yeah. - Thanks for the call.

1248
01:31:09,150 --> 01:31:12,880
- 是你告诉他们的？\n- 这对每个人都有好处，莎莉
- You called them? - It's best for everyone, Sally.

1249
01:31:13,520 --> 01:31:16,650
对每个人都好还是对你好？
Best for everyone or best for you?

1250
01:31:33,140 --> 01:31:35,940
我还没有和他说再见呢
I didn't get to say goodbye to him.

1251
01:32:35,500 --> 01:32:38,840
大家好，赛车迷们
Hello, race fans. Welcome to what has become, quite simply,

1252
01:32:38,910 --> 01:32:41,200
欢迎来到赛车史上最重要的比赛
the biggest event in the history of racing.

1253
01:32:41,280 --> 01:32:43,510
三辆赛车争夺活塞杯！
A three-way battle for the Piston Cup!

1254
01:32:43,580 --> 01:32:46,050
洛杉矶国际赛道涌进了
There's a crowd of nearly 200,000 cars

1255
01:32:46,110 --> 01:32:48,670
大约20万辆赛车迷
here at the Los Angeles International Speedway.

1256
01:32:48,750 --> 01:32:53,080
比赛的票比夏天坐在黑色的皮椅上还要热！
Tickets to this race are hotter than a black leather seat on a hot summer day!

1257
01:32:53,150 --> 01:32:55,710
“国王”，“路霸”和“闪电”麦坤
The King, Chick Hicks and Lightning McQueen

1258
01:32:55,790 --> 01:32:59,120
要赛200圈，胜者将赢得所有的荣誉
in a 200 lap, winner-takes-all, tiebreaker race.

1259
01:32:59,190 --> 01:33:02,420
你知道我见过世面，但让我告诉你
I got a lotta miles on me, but let me tell you somethin'.

1260
01:33:02,500 --> 01:33:06,490
我从来没有想过会看到这场比赛！\n太激动人心了！
I never thought I'd see anything like this. This is exciting!

1261
01:33:06,570 --> 01:33:08,900
事实上，整个国家几乎都歇业了
In fact, the country has almost shut down

1262
01:33:08,970 --> 01:33:13,070
他们都在观看这场世纪之战
to watch what many experts are calling "the race of the century."

1263
01:33:13,140 --> 01:33:15,770
嘿，“国王”，祝你最后一场比赛好运
Hey, King! Good luck in your last race.

1264
01:33:15,840 --> 01:33:19,940
- 我受了你很大的影响\n- 谢谢你，非常感谢
- You've sure been an inspiration to me. - Thanks, Junior. Appreciate it.

1265
01:33:20,010 --> 01:33:23,110
- 你要小心，知道吗？\n- 知道了
- Hey, be careful out there, OK? - Yeah, man.

1266
01:33:23,180 --> 01:33:24,170
他真性感！
He's hot!

1267
01:33:24,250 --> 01:33:26,910
你想要知道天气预报吗？我就告诉你们
Wanna know the forecast? I'll give you the forecast.

1268
01:33:26,990 --> 01:33:30,080
百分之百雷鸣！咔嚓！咔嚓！
A 100 percent chance of thunder! Ka-chicka! Ka-chicka!

1269
01:33:30,160 --> 01:33:32,680
跟我说！咔嚓！咔嚓！
Say it with me! Ka-chicka! Ka-chicka!

1270
01:33:32,760 --> 01:33:35,700
嘿，说你呢！没有证件不能进
Hey, you! No admittance without a garage pass.

1271
01:33:35,760 --> 01:33:38,530
没关系，“闪电”麦坤认识我
Oh, it's OK. Lightning McQueen knows me!

1272
01:33:38,600 --> 01:33:41,730
马克，这天真适合比赛，对不对？
Hey, Marco, it's a beautiful day for a race, isn't it?

1273
01:33:41,800 --> 01:33:46,760
- 是的，安杰帝先生\n- 早，佛瑞德
- Absolutely, Mr. Andretti. - And good morning to you, Fred.

1274
01:33:46,840 --> 01:33:50,740
安杰帝先生知道我的名字！你得让我进去了
Mario Andretti knows my name! You gotta let me in now!

1275
01:33:50,810 --> 01:33:52,070
不好意思，不行
Sorry, pal.

1276
01:33:52,150 --> 01:33:56,410
好了，我们走\n专注，速度
OK, here we go. Focus. Speed.

1277
01:33:57,180 --> 01:33:59,980
我就是速度
I am speed.

1278
01:34:01,720 --> 01:34:02,920
胜利
Victory.

1279
01:34:02,990 --> 01:34:05,120
一个冠军，两个失败者
One winner, two losers.

1280
01:34:07,230 --> 01:34:12,760
速度，速度，速度
Speed. Speed. Speed. Speed...

1281
01:34:17,940 --> 01:34:19,530
“闪电”，准备好了吗？
Lightnin'! You ready?

1282
01:34:19,610 --> 01:34:22,300
是的，准备好了
Yeah, yeah, yeah! I'm ready.

1283
01:34:35,660 --> 01:34:38,490
麦大叔，谢谢你今天当我的维修团队
Mack, thanks for being my pit crew today.

1284
01:34:38,560 --> 01:34:41,150
没关系，小子\n至少我可以帮你做这些
Don't worry about it, kid. It's the least I could do.

1285
01:34:41,230 --> 01:34:43,630
毕竟，油箱是我的中名
After all, "Gas Can" is my middle name.

1286
01:34:43,700 --> 01:34:46,060
- 是吗？\n- 呃...不是真的
- It is? - Ah... Not really.

1287
01:35:03,350 --> 01:35:04,750
额
Uh-oh

1288
01:35:15,630 --> 01:35:18,600
放大！准备切换16号摄影机
Nelson! Zoom in. Ready, 16? Take 16.

1289
01:35:18,770 --> 01:35:21,000
那就是“闪电'麦坤
And there he is, Lightning McQueen!

1290
01:35:21,070 --> 01:35:24,200
失踪了一周，但又从一个\n不知名的地方冒了出来！
Missing all week, and then he turns up in the middle of nowhere!

1291
01:35:24,270 --> 01:35:26,670
一个叫水乡温泉镇的地方
In a little town called Radiator Springs.

1292
01:35:26,740 --> 01:35:29,800
换了白色轮胎和其它装饰
Wearin' whitewall tires, of all things.

1293
01:35:30,950 --> 01:35:34,070
- 哦！\n- 咔嚓！咔嚓！咔嚓！
- Oh! - Ka-chicka! Ka-chicka! Ka-chicka!

1294
01:35:35,380 --> 01:35:37,710
你去哪了，麦坤\n我真是寂寞
Hey, where you been? I've been kinda lonely.

1295
01:35:37,790 --> 01:35:40,690
没有人和我说话\n除了迪纳哥的人
Nobody to hang out with. I mean, except the Dinoco folks.

1296
01:35:40,750 --> 01:35:43,750
当然还有那对双胞胎姐妹\n记得吗，她们是你忠实的粉丝
And the twins. Of course. The ones that used to be your fans,

1297
01:35:43,820 --> 01:35:46,990
现在她们是我的粉丝了\n你知道她们说什么吗
but now they're my fans. Listen to what the twins think...

1298
01:35:53,830 --> 01:35:55,890
啊！
Agh! Shoot!

1299
01:35:55,970 --> 01:35:59,100
伙计们，我们开始比赛吧！
Boogity, boogity, boogity, boys! Let's go racin'!

1300
01:36:05,380 --> 01:36:06,940
你可以做到的！
Come on, you can do it!

1301
01:36:07,010 --> 01:36:09,040
加油，“国王”，我们为你感到骄傲
Come on, King, make us proud, boy!

1302
01:36:10,250 --> 01:36:13,450
50圈了，冠军还保持领先地位
Fifty laps down, and The King is still holding a slim lead.

1303
01:36:13,520 --> 01:36:16,750
麦坤要超车了！他要从内道超车
McQueen's got a run on him! He's lookin' to the inside!

1304
01:36:18,930 --> 01:36:21,090
哦，他阻止了他！
Oh! Chick slammed the door on him!

1305
01:36:21,160 --> 01:36:23,560
“路霸”今天可不是好欺负的
Chick's not making it easy on him today.

1306
01:36:23,630 --> 01:36:25,360
他落后了很长一段距离
He lost momentum,

1307
01:36:25,430 --> 01:36:27,730
他现在要追赶上去！
and now he's gonna have to chase him back down!

1308
01:36:37,140 --> 01:36:39,200
麦坤失去控制，滑到草地上去了！
McQueen spins out in the infield!

1309
01:36:43,180 --> 01:36:45,780
只剩我和那辆老爷车了
Just me and the old man, fellas.

1310
01:36:45,850 --> 01:36:49,380
麦坤今天不在状态
- McQueen just doesn't have it today.

1311
01:36:50,560 --> 01:36:54,620
- 孩子，你还好吗？\n- 我不知道，麦大叔
- Hey, kid, are you all right? - I don't know, Mack.

1312
01:36:54,700 --> 01:36:56,130
我想我
I don't think I...

1313
01:36:56,200 --> 01:36:58,930
我可不是开可这么远的路来看你退出的
I didn't come all this way to see you quit.

1314
01:36:59,170 --> 01:37:00,690
韩大夫？
Doc?

1315
01:37:03,370 --> 01:37:06,000
伙计们，你们都来了！\n真不敢相信！
Guys, you're here! I can't believe this!

1316
01:37:06,070 --> 01:37:09,840
我知道你需要一个车队主管\n但我不知道你这么烂
I knew you needed a crew chief, but I didn't know it was this bad.

1317
01:37:09,910 --> 01:37:11,810
你说你永远不会回来了
You said you'd never come back.

1318
01:37:11,880 --> 01:37:15,470
好吧，我没有选择的余地\n拖线没有和你说再见
Well, I really didn't have a choice. Mater didn't get to say goodbye.

1319
01:37:15,550 --> 01:37:18,450
再见！好了，没我事了
Goodbye! OK, I'm good.

1320
01:37:22,420 --> 01:37:25,920
如果你能像你修路时那样驾驶
All right, if you can drive as good as you can fix a road

1321
01:37:25,990 --> 01:37:29,260
就算你闭着眼也能赢这场比赛
then you can win this race with your eyes shut.

1322
01:37:29,330 --> 01:37:31,320
回到比赛去吧！
Now, get back out there!

1323
01:37:33,570 --> 01:37:36,540
他终于恢复状态了！\n奇诺，路易奇
Hot snot, we are back in business! Guido! Luigi!

1324
01:37:36,600 --> 01:37:38,900
你们如果要和专业的维修团队竞争
You're goin' up against professional pit crews.

1325
01:37:38,970 --> 01:37:42,140
- 你们的动作必须要快\n- 他们根本都不知道他们为什么输了！
- You're gonna have to be fast. - They will not know what bit them!

1326
01:37:42,210 --> 01:37:43,900
孩子，你一定会赢他们的
Kid, you can beat these guys.

1327
01:37:43,980 --> 01:37:47,380
最好的队员和你合作\n你会夺回那一圈的差距的
Find a groove that works for you and get that lap back.

1328
01:37:59,090 --> 01:38:00,990
- 是他？\n- 哦，没错，就是他！
- Is it? - Oh, wow. That's him!

1329
01:38:01,060 --> 01:38:04,830
是他吗？那是哈德逊大黄蜂！\n哈德逊大黄蜂回来了！
Is that...? That's the Hudson Hornet! The Hudson Hornet's back!

1330
01:38:04,900 --> 01:38:07,530
看上去麦坤有了自己的维修团队
It appears McQueen has got himself a pit crew.

1331
01:38:07,600 --> 01:38:10,000
看看他们的主管是谁
And look who he has for a crew chief!

1332
01:38:10,070 --> 01:38:12,770
- 快看，是哈德逊大黄蜂！\n- 哇！
- Look, man. It's the Hudson Hornet! - Whoa!

1333
01:38:12,840 --> 01:38:16,170
真是太棒了，当然是他
Well, dip me in axle grease and call me Slick! It surely is.

1334
01:38:20,810 --> 01:38:22,840
这真是在制造历史
Wow, this is history in the making.

1335
01:38:22,920 --> 01:38:25,820
50年来，有人见过这位赛车界的传奇人物
Nobody has seen the racing legend in over 50 years!

1336
01:38:25,890 --> 01:38:27,290
嘿，韩大夫
Hey, Doc!

1337
01:38:27,350 --> 01:38:31,520
快看看这位在广播上的人\n他看起来就像你
Come look at this fellow on the radio. He looks just like you.

1338
01:38:36,430 --> 01:38:40,230
- 麦坤在内道超车了\n- 但是他还落后一圈
- McQueen passes on the inside! - He's nearly a lap down.

1339
01:38:40,300 --> 01:38:43,200
还剩60圈，他能赶上他们吗？
Can he catch up to them with only 60 laps to go?

1340
01:38:43,270 --> 01:38:46,170
你做的很好，要保持下去
You're goin' great, kid. Just keep your head on.

1341
01:38:46,240 --> 01:38:47,830
加油！加油！
Vai! Vai, vai!

1342
01:38:47,910 --> 01:38:50,810
嘿，麦坤在哪里找到你的？
Hey, shrimpie, where did McQueen find you, huh?

1343
01:38:50,880 --> 01:38:54,310
那些圆的东西叫轮胎\n它们应该放在车子下面
Those round things are called tires, and they go under the car!

1344
01:38:55,480 --> 01:38:58,080
[意大利语]
Con chi credi di parlare? Ma, con chi stai parlando?

1345
01:38:58,150 --> 01:39:01,320
不不不！你会有机会表现的
No! No, no! You'll have your chance. You will have your chance.

1346
01:39:15,770 --> 01:39:18,570
这小子想成为英雄吗？
Oh, kid's just tryin' to be a hero, huh?

1347
01:39:20,140 --> 01:39:21,400
看看这个怎么样？
What do you think of this?

1348
01:39:21,480 --> 01:39:23,640
对，就是这样，孩子
Yeah, that's it, kid.

1349
01:39:26,950 --> 01:39:28,240
什么？
What?

1350
01:39:28,320 --> 01:39:30,110
哇！就是这样！
Whoa! Git-R-done!

1351
01:39:31,890 --> 01:39:36,150
- 是我教他的！咔嚓！\n- 啊！
- I taught him that. Ka-chow! - Ah!

1352
01:39:36,220 --> 01:39:39,190
麦坤真是太棒了\n他已经追上领跑者了
What a move by McQueen! He's caught up to the leaders.

1353
01:39:39,260 --> 01:39:41,090
这才是最关键的
Yeah. This is what it's all about.

1354
01:39:41,160 --> 01:39:44,320
3辆车的比赛，还剩下10圈
A three-way battle for the lead, with ten to go!

1355
01:39:47,970 --> 01:39:51,170
看看在跑的那小子
Look at that boy go out there!

1356
01:39:56,880 --> 01:39:59,180
啊！
Oh!

1357
01:40:00,110 --> 01:40:01,670
不，这可不行！
No, you don't.

1358
01:40:04,750 --> 01:40:06,740
韩大夫，我暴胎了！我暴胎了！
Doc, I'm flat! I'm flat!

1359
01:40:06,820 --> 01:40:10,260
- 你能开到维修站吗？\n- 我想没问题
- Can you get back to the pits? - Yeah, yeah. I think so.

1360
01:40:10,320 --> 01:40:13,620
亮黄旗了，快开进来，不要失去信心
Hey, got a yellow. Bring it in. Don't tear yourself up, kid.

1361
01:40:15,560 --> 01:40:17,690
我们必须马上把他修好
We gotta get him back out there fast

1362
01:40:17,760 --> 01:40:20,700
不然我们不可能赢这场比赛！
or we're gonna be a lap down, and we'll never win this race!

1363
01:40:20,770 --> 01:40:22,930
奇诺，时间到了
Guido! It's time.

1364
01:40:27,210 --> 01:40:30,300
小不点，你要帮他擦挡风玻璃吗？
Hey, tiny, you gonna clean his windshield?

1365
01:40:39,420 --> 01:40:40,850
真是不敢相信！
I don't believe it!

1366
01:40:40,920 --> 01:40:42,620
那是我见过的最快的换胎过程！
That was the fastest pit stop I've ever seen!

1367
01:40:42,690 --> 01:40:45,250
漂亮的停站\n但是他必须超过那辆安全车
It was a great stop, but he's still gotta beat that pace car!

1368
01:40:45,330 --> 01:40:47,020
接近了
It's gonna be close.

1369
01:40:48,700 --> 01:40:51,160
太棒了，伙计
- Yeah, baby!

1370
01:40:51,230 --> 01:40:52,600
他又回来了！
He's back in!

1371
01:40:53,930 --> 01:40:54,920
换胎完毕
Peet stop.

1372
01:40:56,370 --> 01:40:58,300
- 奇诺，你成功了！\n- 干得好，奇诺！
- Guido, you did it! - Way to go, Guido!

1373
01:41:13,590 --> 01:41:16,650
我们即将进入最后一圈
This is it. We're heading into the final lap and McQueen

1374
01:41:16,720 --> 01:41:19,090
麦坤就跟在他们后边，多棒的回归
is right behind the leaders. What a comeback!

1375
01:41:19,160 --> 01:41:22,690
199圈了，已经到了最关键的时刻
A hundred and ninety-nine laps! It all comes down to this!

1376
01:41:22,760 --> 01:41:24,030
就是这样，孩子
This is it, kiddo.

1377
01:41:24,100 --> 01:41:26,590
就剩下4个弯脚了，一个一个的来
You've got four turns left. One at a time.

1378
01:41:26,670 --> 01:41:29,100
加速猛冲，希望你不会失控
Drive it in deep and hope it sticks.

1379
01:41:29,170 --> 01:41:30,570
冲啊！
- Go!

1380
01:41:33,270 --> 01:41:34,400
瞧瞧这个！
We'll see about that!

1381
01:41:35,910 --> 01:41:37,470
麦坤在内道超车
McQueen's going inside!

1382
01:41:40,450 --> 01:41:43,470
- “国王”和“路霸”失控了\n- 麦坤滑出了赛道！
- Chick and King are loose! - I think McQueen's out!

1383
01:41:54,160 --> 01:41:56,630
- 麦坤又回来了！\n- 他回到了赛道！
- McQueen saved it! - He's back on the track!

1384
01:41:57,030 --> 01:41:59,690
- 壮如凯迪拉克\n- 快如宝马
- Float like a Cadillac... - Sting like a Beemer!

1385
01:42:00,770 --> 01:42:04,400
咔嚓！咔嚓！咔...
- Ka-chow! Ka-chow! Ka...

1386
01:42:05,970 --> 01:42:08,970
“闪电”麦坤即将赢得活塞杯了
Lightning McQueen is gonna win the Piston Cup!

1387
01:42:09,040 --> 01:42:11,140
你一定会赢的！一定会
Come on! You got it! You got it, Stickers!

1388
01:42:12,650 --> 01:42:16,450
我不会再跟在你屁股后面开了，老家伙
I am not comin' in behind you again, old man.

1389
01:42:26,790 --> 01:42:28,690
哦，不！
- Oh, no!

1390
01:42:47,210 --> 01:42:49,410
耶！哇！
Yeah! Whoo-hoo!

1391
01:42:49,480 --> 01:42:53,210
我赢了，宝贝！耶！哦耶！
I won, baby! Yeah! Oh, yeah!

1392
01:42:54,520 --> 01:42:56,650
他到底想干什么，韩大夫？
What's he up to, Doc?

1393
01:43:07,030 --> 01:43:08,400
你要干什么，孩子？
What are you doin', kid?

1394
01:43:08,470 --> 01:43:11,700
我想“国王”应该完成\n他的最后一场比赛
I think The King should finish his last race.

1395
01:43:14,880 --> 01:43:17,870
你刚刚放弃了活塞杯，你知道吗？
You just gave up the Piston Cup, you know that?

1396
01:43:17,940 --> 01:43:21,540
有一辆老赛车教会了我一些事
This grumpy old racecar I know once told me somethin'.

1397
01:43:21,620 --> 01:43:23,670
那只是一个没用的杯子
It's just an empty cup.

1398
01:43:25,790 --> 01:43:28,350
在最后一圈推车符合赛规吗？
Darrell, is pushing on the last lap legal?

1399
01:43:28,420 --> 01:43:32,090
他没有在推，他只是跟在他后边开而已
He's not really pushin' him. He's just givin' him a little bump draft.

1400
01:43:32,160 --> 01:43:34,460
喔！哦哦哦哦！
Whoo-hoo-hoo-hoo-hoo!

1401
01:43:34,530 --> 01:43:37,220
嘿，发生了什么事？
Hey. What? What's goin' on?

1402
01:43:37,300 --> 01:43:39,560
那才叫真正的赛车！
- That's what I call racin'.

1403
01:43:55,520 --> 01:43:58,580
- [意大利语]\n- 做的太好了
- Bravo il mio amico! - Way to go, buddy!

1404
01:43:58,650 --> 01:44:01,250
这里充满了爱，不是吗？
There's a lotta love out there, you know, man?

1405
01:44:01,320 --> 01:44:05,850
- 不要让我丢脸\n- 那才是我喜欢的赛车
- Don't embarrass me, Fillmore. - That's my hot rod.

1406
01:44:07,890 --> 01:44:11,330
快点，把活塞杯给我
Come on, baby, bring it out! Bring out the Piston Cup!

1407
01:44:11,400 --> 01:44:12,800
咔嚓！咔嚓！
Ka-chicka! Ka-chicka!

1408
01:44:12,870 --> 01:44:15,840
耶！这就是我想要的！
Yeah! Now, that's what I'm talkin' about!

1409
01:44:15,900 --> 01:44:19,030
嘿，为什么只有我自己在庆祝？
Hey, how come the only one celebrating is me, huh?

1410
01:44:19,110 --> 01:44:21,340
女孩们呢？彩纸呢？
Where are the girls? Bring on the confetti!

1411
01:44:21,410 --> 01:44:25,000
喔！喔！轻一点！怎么了？
Ow! Ow! Easy with the confetti. What's goin' on?

1412
01:44:25,080 --> 01:44:28,380
快照些照片\n我要去和迪纳哥签合同了！
Come on, snap some pictures. I gotta go sign my deal with Dinoco!

1413
01:44:28,450 --> 01:44:29,920
跟着我一起说，咔嚓！
Say it with me. Ka-chicka!

1414
01:44:30,080 --> 01:44:31,610
- 嘘！\n- 嘘！
- Boo! - Boo!

1415
01:44:31,690 --> 01:44:34,780
你们都怎么了？到底怎么了？
What's wrong with everybody? Where's the happiness?

1416
01:44:34,860 --> 01:44:36,950
嘿！这可是奇克时代的开始啊！
Hey! This is the start of the Chick era!

1417
01:44:42,860 --> 01:44:45,350
- 谢谢你，“闪电”\n- 不客气
- Thanks, Lightnin'. - You're welcome.

1418
01:44:47,770 --> 01:44:50,200
- 干的好，“国王”\n- 你是好样的！
- Way to go, King! - You're still the car!

1419
01:44:50,270 --> 01:44:52,260
你才是真正的冠军！
You're The King! Yeah!

1420
01:45:02,680 --> 01:45:06,140
- 我们为你感到骄傲，孩子！\n- 祝贺你，小子
- You made us proud, kid! - Congrats on the loss, me bucko!

1421
01:45:09,360 --> 01:45:11,980
你很有潜力，孩子
You got a lotta stuff, kid.

1422
01:45:12,190 --> 01:45:13,850
谢谢你，韩大夫
Thanks, Doc.

1423
01:45:15,000 --> 01:45:16,330
嘿，“闪电”
Hey, Lightnin'.

1424
01:45:16,400 --> 01:45:19,060
过来和我谈一谈怎么样？
How 'bout comin' over here and talk to me a minute?

1425
01:45:19,970 --> 01:45:22,990
孩子，这才是真正的比赛
Son, that was some real racin' out there.

1426
01:45:23,070 --> 01:45:25,830
你想不想成为迪纳哥新的代言人？
How'd you like to become the new face of Dinoco?

1427
01:45:30,540 --> 01:45:32,010
但是我没有赢
But I didn't win.

1428
01:45:32,080 --> 01:45:35,740
“闪电”，除了赢得比赛之外\n还有其它更重要的事
Lightnin', there's a whole lot more to racin' than just winnin'.

1429
01:45:35,820 --> 01:45:38,510
你看他都生锈了\n他需要“除锈灵”保险杠防锈药膏
He was so rusty, when he drove down the street

1430
01:45:38,590 --> 01:45:42,750
围着车绕圈子
- buzzards used to circle the car!

1431
01:45:42,820 --> 01:45:44,550
感谢你，泰克思先生，但是
Thank you, Mr. Tex, but...

1432
01:45:44,620 --> 01:45:48,360
但是“除锈灵”保险杠防锈药膏的人\n给了我第一次机会
...but these Rust-eze guys over there gave me my big break.

1433
01:45:49,900 --> 01:45:51,630
我想和他们在一起
I'm gonna stick with them.

1434
01:45:51,700 --> 01:45:54,760
我尊重你的决定
Well, I sure can respect that.

1435
01:45:54,840 --> 01:45:56,000
可是你知道
Still, you know,

1436
01:45:56,070 --> 01:45:59,940
如果有任何事需要帮忙\n告诉我就可以了
if there's ever anything I can do for you, just let me know.

1437
01:46:00,010 --> 01:46:02,530
我很感激，谢谢你
I sure appreciate that. Thank you.

1438
01:46:04,010 --> 01:46:07,000
实际上，有一件事
Actually, there is one thing.

1439
01:46:07,710 --> 01:46:08,720
哇喔！
Whoo-hoo!

1440
01:46:08,720 --> 01:46:09,940
哇喔！
Whoo-hoo!

1441
01:46:10,020 --> 01:46:13,880
嘿！看看我！我在飞！
Hey, look at me! I'm flyin', by golly!

1442
01:46:18,390 --> 01:46:21,380
我比在停车场的“龙卷风”还要开心
I'm happier than a tornado in a trailer park!

1443
01:46:25,030 --> 01:46:27,330
我们是不是该重新装修一下了
I think it's about-a time we redecorate.

1444
01:46:30,470 --> 01:46:33,910
你好，“闪电”麦坤告诉我\n这是世界上最好的
Hi. Lightning McQueen told me this was the best place in the world

1445
01:46:33,970 --> 01:46:34,960
轮胎店
to get tires.

1446
01:46:35,040 --> 01:46:39,240
给我和我的朋友换一换轮胎怎么样？
How 'bout setting me and my friends up with three or four sets each?

1447
01:46:39,310 --> 01:46:44,510
奇诺，这是真正的舒马赫的法拉利！
Guido! There is a real Michael Schumacher Ferrari in my store.

1448
01:46:44,580 --> 01:46:46,880
一辆真正的法拉利！
A real Ferrari!

1449
01:46:46,950 --> 01:46:49,080
在我脸上打一拳，奇诺，打一拳
Punch me, Guido. Punch me in the face.

1450
01:46:49,160 --> 01:46:52,610
这是我生命中最美好的一天
This is the most glorious day of my life.

1451
01:46:53,930 --> 01:46:57,490
哇[意大利语]
Wow. [Italian] Spero che il tuo amico si riprenda.

1452
01:46:57,560 --> 01:46:59,900
[意大利语]
Mi dicono che siete fantastici.

1453
01:47:16,180 --> 01:47:17,710
只是路过吗？
Just passin' through?

1454
01:47:17,780 --> 01:47:20,080
其实我想在这里呆一段时间
Actually, I thought I'd stop and stay awhile.

1455
01:47:20,150 --> 01:47:23,420
- 我听说这个地方又在地图上出现了\n- 是吗？
- I hear this place is back on the map. - It is?

1456
01:47:23,490 --> 01:47:27,260
有人说一个活塞杯获得者
There's some rumor floating around that some hotshot Piston Cup racecar

1457
01:47:27,330 --> 01:47:29,800
会在这里建立他的比赛中心
is setting up his big racing headquarters here.

1458
01:47:29,860 --> 01:47:32,700
真的吗？这对小镇来说是件大好事
Really? Ah, well, there goes the town.

1459
01:47:32,770 --> 01:47:35,260
我很想你，莎莉
You know, I really missed you, Sally.

1460
01:47:35,340 --> 01:47:39,470
我有一种别人并不理解的感觉
Well, I create feelings in others they themselves don't understand and,

1461
01:47:39,540 --> 01:47:41,700
等等等
- blah, blah, blah.

1462
01:47:42,110 --> 01:47:45,100
麦坤和莎莉停在树旁边
McQueen and Sally parked beneath the tree,

1463
01:47:45,180 --> 01:47:49,810
亲亲...亲亲...
K- i-s-s... uh... i- n-t!

1464
01:47:50,180 --> 01:47:52,150
拖线，来的真是时候
Great timing, Mater!

1465
01:47:52,220 --> 01:47:56,210
嘿嘿！耶！
Hep-non, hip-hep, hi-li-lilly! Whee!

1466
01:47:56,290 --> 01:47:58,720
他是我最好的朋友\n我能拿他怎么办呢？
He's my best friend. What're you gonna do?

1467
01:47:58,790 --> 01:48:01,730
那么，准备最后一个光顾芙蓉的店？
So, Stickers, last one to Flo's buys?

1468
01:48:01,800 --> 01:48:04,490
我不知道，我们为什么不去兜兜风
I don't know. Why don't we just take a drive?

1469
01:48:04,560 --> 01:48:07,160
嗯...不
Hmm... Nah.

1470
01:48:08,900 --> 01:48:11,140
好吧！咔嚓！
Yeah! Ka-chow!

1471
01:49:16,200 --> 01:49:20,200
阿嚏！
Ah-choo!

1472
01:49:23,010 --> 01:49:26,000
大家过来集合一下
All right, everybody please keep together now.

1473
01:49:26,080 --> 01:49:30,850
我们现在进入了韩大夫博物馆
We is now entering the Doc Hudson wing of the museum.

1474
01:49:30,920 --> 01:49:33,890
哇，太不可思议了，一个赛季拿这么多冠军
Wow. Unbelievable. That many wins in a single season.

1475
01:49:33,950 --> 01:49:38,010
他实在太厉害了，哈德逊大黄蜂是我的偶像
He's the real deal, Junior. The Hudson Hornet was my inspiration.

1476
01:49:38,090 --> 01:49:41,550
打扰了，哈德逊大黄蜂今天在吗？
Excuse me, son. Is Doc Hudson here today?

1477
01:49:41,630 --> 01:49:45,430
抱歉，“国王”夫人，我想韩大夫可能是出去兜风了
Sorry, Mrs. The King, I think Doc went out for a drive or somethin'.

1478
01:49:48,770 --> 01:49:51,930
- 哇哦！哇哦！\n- 耶！
- Whoo! Whoo! - Yeah!

1479
01:49:52,000 --> 01:49:54,530
嘿，你可不是开泥地的
Well, you sure ain't no dirt boy.

1480
01:49:54,610 --> 01:49:57,670
老家伙，泥的绝招我可都会了
Not today, old man. I know all your tricks.

1481
01:50:01,950 --> 01:50:03,880
韩大夫！韩大夫！
Doc! Doc!

1482
01:50:04,180 --> 01:50:05,650
喔哈！
Whoo-ah!

1483
01:50:06,120 --> 01:50:08,310
差远啦，菜鸟！
Not all my tricks, rookie!

1484
01:50:24,940 --> 01:50:28,430
注意！和公路吻别吧
Attention! Kiss the pavement goodbye.

1485
01:50:28,510 --> 01:50:31,940
等我搞定后，你们会在\n想象不到的地方沾上泥土
When I'm finished, you'll have mud in places you didn't know you had!

1486
01:50:32,010 --> 01:50:35,850
- 啊，我从来没在路外面开过呢\n- 好吧，那现在你得改改了
- Yo, I've never been off-road! - Well, that's gonna change right now!

1487
01:50:36,120 --> 01:50:39,020
向后转！往前开20英里！
About face! Drop and give me 20 miles!

1488
01:50:39,080 --> 01:50:41,080
出发！出发！开！开！开！开！开！
Go! Go! Go, go, go, go, go! Go!

1489
01:50:41,150 --> 01:50:43,990
伙计，我的轮胎脏了！
Man, now I got dirt in my rims!

1490
01:50:46,630 --> 01:50:48,620
嗯？看啊！
Huh? Look at this!

1491
01:50:48,690 --> 01:50:50,860
这是我的前盖！我的前盖！
It's my hood! It's my hood!

1492
01:50:50,930 --> 01:50:54,020
我已经20年没见到它了！
I ain't seen this thing in 20 years!

1493
01:50:54,630 --> 01:50:58,590
看上去太棒了，我看上去怎么样？\n阿嚏！
Well, it fits perfectly. How do I look? Ah-choo!

1494
01:51:04,280 --> 01:51:05,540
哦，天啊
Oh, dang.

1495
01:51:10,720 --> 01:51:14,240
你是一辆玩具车！
You are a toy car!

1496
01:51:14,320 --> 01:51:19,090
你就是辆可怜的，古怪的破车\n我还真同情你，再见
You are a sad, strange little wagon and you have my pity. Farewell.

1497
01:51:19,490 --> 01:51:22,220
哦，是吗？好吧，随你吧，疯子
Oh, yeah? Well, good riddance, you loony!

1498
01:51:22,290 --> 01:51:25,990
嘿，我可不想打断集会\n但伙计们，他们来了！
Hey, I hate to break up the road rally, guys, but they're here!

1499
01:51:26,070 --> 01:51:28,430
三点参加生日聚会的客人们！
Birthday guests at three o'clock!

1500
01:51:28,500 --> 01:51:31,830
伙计们！谁要能像这只卡车猪那样说话
Oh, man! Whoever does the voice of that piggy truck,

1501
01:51:31,900 --> 01:51:34,460
我敢保证他是个很棒的演员！
I'm tellin' ya, he's one great actor!

1502
01:51:35,010 --> 01:51:39,210
我们被流放了，天才们！\n被困在这个鬼地方！
We're banished, genius! Stuck here in this wasteland without chains!

1503
01:51:39,280 --> 01:51:43,040
但是麦克，波波比尔还有麻烦\n她需要我们的帮助！
But, Mike, the Boomobile's in trouble! She needs our help!

1504
01:51:43,120 --> 01:51:47,380
- 你还是没在听我说话！\n- 啊！
- You're still not listening!  - Ah!

1505
01:51:47,450 --> 01:51:51,080
欢迎来到喜马拉雅山！要冰激凌吗？
Welcome to the Himalayas! Snow cone?

1506
01:51:51,390 --> 01:51:55,090
哦，这辆扫雪机还真有意思
Oh, that Abominable Snowplow is quite the comic thespian!

1507
01:51:55,630 --> 01:51:57,620
快进去吧！快快快！
Just get in there. Go! Go, go, go!

1508
01:51:57,700 --> 01:51:59,100
马戏车？
Circus cars?

1509
01:51:59,160 --> 01:52:01,630
你们是怎么成为马戏车的？
How can you be circus cars?

1510
01:52:01,700 --> 01:52:04,230
这些可是世界上最有意思的马戏车
These are the lousiest circus cars in the world,

1511
01:52:04,300 --> 01:52:06,290
他们会让我成为富翁！
and they're gonna make me rich!

1512
01:52:06,370 --> 01:52:07,500
等一下！
Wait a minute here.

1513
01:52:07,570 --> 01:52:10,040
他们演来演去就这几个人
They're just usin' the same actor over and over.

1514
01:52:10,110 --> 01:52:12,670
真是粗制滥造！
What kind of a cut-rate production is this?

1515
01:55:38,520 --> 01:55:43,180
哦，老天啊，我们能找个人问问路吗？
Oh, for the love of Chrysler, can we please ask someone for directions?

1516
01:55:43,260 --> 01:55:47,490
不！我们马上就要到达营地了！我知道的！我能感觉到！
No! There's an on-ramp close! I know it! I can feel it!

